Umubare w'abarwayi ba coronavirus (COVID-19) wiyongereye cyane mu Burayi/mu Burayi n'u Bwongereza, kuva ku ya 1 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020
Iyo abantu bose banduye coronavirus (COVID-19) bagaragaje ibimenyetso bimwe mu bihugu by'i Burayi/mu Burayi n'u Bwongereza, byemeza ko nubwo ibipimo by'ubwandu bitandukanye bitewe n'ibihugu, icyorezo cya COVID-19 gishobora gukwirakwira mu buryo bwihuse mu bihugu byose.
Ukurikije ibyabaye mu Butaliyani, ibihugu, ibitaro n'ibigo byita ku barwayi bazima bikeneye cyane guhangana n'umubare munini w'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakeneye ubuvuzi, cyane cyane mu byumba by'indembe.
Ku ya 31 Ukuboza 2019, abantu benshi bagaragaweho indwara y'ubuhumekero idasanzwe mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu ntara ya Hubei, mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 9 Mutarama 2020, Ikigo cy'Ubushinwa gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara cyatangaje ko iyi ndwara yatewe n'ubwoko bushya bwa koronavirusi ubu bwitwa SARS-CoV-2.
Kuva icyo gihe, indwara iterwa na SARS-CoV-2 yatangiye kwitwa indwara y'agakoko ka koronavirusi (COVID-19).
Ibihamya dufite ubu bigaragaza ko 80% by'abantu banduye COVID-19 bafite uburwayi bworoheje, nk'indwara y'ubuhumekero cyangwa guhumeka nabi, kandi abenshi muri bo barakira.
Mu bantu 14%, COVID-19 iterwa n'uburwayi bukabije bukenera kuvurwa mu bitaro, mu gihe 6% by'abanduye iba ikomeye cyane igasaba kwitabwaho mu bitaro byagutse.
Umubare w'abapfa mu gihe cy'ibitaro bazira COVID-19 ni 4%.
Muri ubu bushakashatsi, tugiye gusuzuma uko ibintu byifashe mu gihe cyose COVID-19 imaze kwaduka mu bihugu byose by'u Burayi/Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi n'u Bwongereza (UK) maze tugereranye n'uko bimeze mu Ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Tuzagereranya kandi imibare y'abanduye COVID-19 muri iki gihe mu Burayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi n'u Bwongereza n'u Butaliyani kuva ku ya 31 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Imibare y'abarwayi ba COVID-19 mu Burayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi no mu Bwongereza
Nk'uko byagenze mu Bushinwa, COVID-19 yakwirakwiriye mu bindi bihugu kandi icyorezo cya COVID-19 kirimo gukwirakwira mu bindi bihugu nk'uko byagenze muri icyo gihugu.
Ku ya 11 Werurwe 2020, Umuyobozi Mukuru w'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) yatangaje ko COVID-19 ari icyorezo.
Ku ya 5 Werurwe 2020, ikinyamakuru cya Eurosurveillance cyasohotsemo raporo ya Spiteri na bagenzi be, ivuga ku bantu ba mbere bo mu Burayi banduye COVID-19 hakurikijwe ibisobanuro bitangwa na OMS.
Mu Burayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi, abantu batatu ba mbere banduye bagaragaye mu Bufaransa ku ya 24 Mutarama 2020; bari abantu bagarutse mu Bufaransa bavuye mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu ntara ya Hubei, mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020, hari hari ibimenyetso bya COVID-19 mu bihugu 30 byose by'u Burayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi no mu Bwongereza (UK), kandi kuva ku ya 31 Ukuboza 2019 kugeza ubu, hari hamaze kuboneka abantu 39,768 banduye n'abantu 1,727 bapfuye, mu Butaliyani gusa hari hamaze kuboneka abantu 17,750 banduye n'abantu 1,441 bapfuye.
Gukurikirana imibare yose n'ibimenyetso by'ubwandu bwa COVID-19
Ikigo cy'u Burayi Gishinzwe Kurwanya no Kurwanya Indwara (ECDC), gitanga imibare y'ubwandu bwa COVID-19 muri buri gihugu, ishingiye gusa ku makuru y'ibanze, urugero nk'ibiro by'ubuzima ku isi, inzego z'ubuzima ku rwego rw'igihugu n'iz'akarere ndetse na OMS, buri munsi saa munani za mu gitondo.
Aya makuru yakoreshejwe mu kumenya uko COVID-19 ikwirakwira mu Burayi/mu Burayi bw'Ubukungu n'u Bwongereza, hagereranywa n'uko byaragenze mu Butaliyani.
Mu rwego rw'ubwandu bwa COVID-19, hashingiwe ku minsi 14 y'ubukonje bw'abantu banduye COVID-19, bityo hashingiwe ku kwiyongera kwa COVID-19 mu bihugu byose by'u Burayi/Mu Burayi n'u Bwongereza, mu gihe kuva ku ya 1 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Twahise dutanga imibare y'ubwandu muri buri gihugu ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe 2020 saa munani za mu gitondo, tugereranyije n'umubare w'abanduye mu Butaliyani kuva ku itariki ya 31 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Imibare y'ubwandu bwa COVID-19 mu Burayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi no mu Bwongereza
Imibare y'ubwandu bw'indwara ya COVID-19 mu minsi 14 mu Burayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi no mu Bwongereza igaragaza ko ibipimo by'ubwandu byakurikiranye mu Ntara ya Hubei (Ubushinwa) (Igishushanyo cya 1).
Mu bihugu byo mu Burayi/mu Burayi n'u Bwongereza, icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyatangiye kwiyongera ahagana ku ya 21 Gashyantare, hanyuma kigera ku rugero ruciriritse ahagana ku ya 28 Gashyantare 2020 (Bindi bisobanuro).
Ibi byatewe ahanini n'umubare munini w'abanduye muri Italy, ariko mu bihugu byose by'i Burayi/mu Burayi, umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 wariyongereye cyane (Ibindi bisobanuro).
Umubare wa 2 ugaragaza umubare w'abantu bose banduye COVID-19, mu bihugu by'i Burayi/Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi n'u Bwongereza ugereranyije n'u Butaliyani kuva ku ya 31 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Ibi bigaragaza ko ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe saa munani za mu gitondo, ibindi bihugu 15 byo mu Burayi/mu Muryango w'Ubukungu w'u Burayi n'u Bwongereza byari bifite umubare w'abanduye ungana n'uw'u Butaliyani mu byumweru bitatu cyangwa birenga.
Ibisubizo byacu byerekana ko umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 uzamuka cyane mu Burayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi no mu Bwongereza.
Ibipimo byafashwe ku bantu bose banduye COVID-19 byerekana ko icyorezo cyakwirakwiriye mu buryo bumwe mu bindi bihugu.
Nubwo ibihugu bifite amategeko atandukanye, abaganga bashobora guhuza uburyo bwo kuvura, kandi rimwe na rimwe bashobora gusobanura indwara mu buryo butandukanye bitewe n'ibihugu n'amategeko mu gihe bahitamo abarwayi bagomba gupimwa COVID-19, ndetse no gupimwa nyuma.
Mu ntangiriro za Werurwe 2020, abaganga bo mu Butaliyani bari mu karere karimo icyorezo bavuze ko 10% by'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakeneye kwitabwaho cyane kandi itangazamakuru ryavuze ko ibitaro byo muri ako karere birimo abantu benshi cyane.
Amakuru y'abantu barwariye mu bitaro na/cyangwa bari mu bitaro byita ku barwayi ba COVID-19 ubu aboneka mu bihugu by'i Burayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi ku bantu 6% na 1% (amakuru ntabwo agaragazwa).
Ariko kandi, ibyo bigomba guhuzwa neza kugira ngo bihuze n'amakuru mashya agaragaza umubare w'abarwayi n'abapfa.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu 2010-11 bwagaragaje ko mu Burayi hari ihinduka rikomeye mu bitaro bya ICU n'ibitanda byo mu cyiciro cyo hagati, aho mu Budage hari ibitanda 29,2 na 4,2 ku baturage 100,000 muri Porutugali.
Ibi bivuze ko ibihugu bishobora kugira ubushobozi bwo kwivuza bufite aho bugarukira kurusha u Butaliyani (ibitanda 12,5 byo kwivuza mu bitaro byagutse n'ibiro by'indembe ku baturage 100,000 mu 201011).
Guteza imbere ubuvuzi bw'abarwayi birenze ibipimo by'ubuvuzi, kuko imibare igaragaza ko mu Burayi bwose/mu Burayi n'u Bwongereza abantu barembye cyane kubera COVID-19 kandi ko bafite &gt; 90% by'ibyago byo kubura ibitanda mu bitaro byita ku barwayi barembye, byatanzwe mu ngingo esheshatu nshya za ECDC ku igenzura ry'ibyago bya COVID-19.
Kubera ko hari umubare munini w'abarwayi mu bice bimwe na bimwe by'u Burayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi no mu Bwongereza, kandi ibitaro byo mu bigo byita ku barwayi bababaye cyane bikunze gukoreshwa mu kwita ku baturage bo mu karere runaka, amakuru yerekeye uburwayi n'ibitanda by'abarwayi bababaye cyane agomba kuboneka mu gice cyitwa Nomenclature of Information Level 2 (NUTS-2).
Amakuru y'ibyabaye mu Butaliyani n'ay'ibizaba mu bindi bihugu bigaragaza ko icyorezo cya COVID-19 kiri kwiyongera mu Burayi/mu Murenge w'Ubukungu w'u Burayi no mu Bwongereza.
Ibihugu, ibitaro n'ibigo byita ku barwayi bazima bikwiye kwitegura guhangana n'ubwandu bwinshi bwa SARS-CoV-2 n'umubare munini w'abarwayi ba COVID-19 basabye ubufasha, cyane cyane mu byumba by'indembe, nk'aho biri mu bice by'u Butaliyani byugarijwe n'icyorezo.
Nk'uko byagaragajwe n'isesengura ry'ibyago riherutse gukorwa na ECDC, uburyo bwihuse, bw'ingirakamaro kandi bw'ingirakamaro ni ngombwa mu guhagarika ikwirakwira rya SARS-COV-2, mu kureka kwita ku bantu banduye no mu kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'ubwandu; kuko kumenya neza uko abantu benshi bazabaho mu gihe kizaza bitafasha abantu gufata ibyemezo kandi ibitaro ntibizabona umwanya wo kubisobanukirwa, kubyakira no kwitegura ku buryo bwo kubigoboka mu gihe bitigeze bigerageza mbere.
Igenzura ryihutirwa ry'ibyago ryerekeza no ku ngamba z'ubuzima rusange zo kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo.
Ibi bituma abantu benshi batamenya uko bakwirakwira, kandi bituma abantu benshi batamenya uko bakwirakwira.
Bitabaye ibyo, inzego z'ubuzima mu bihugu bimwe na bimwe by'u Burayi/Ubumwe bw'u Burayi zishobora guhura n'ikibazo cy'ubwandu bukabije kandi bigasaba ko abantu bashyirwa mu bitaro byita ku barwayi mu minsi cyangwa mu byumweru biri imbere.
Icyorezo cya coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19), cyatewe n'indwara y'ibicurane bikomeye (SARS) coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2), kimaze guhitana abantu barenga 3,000 no kwanduza abantu barenga 80,000 mu Bushinwa no mu bindi bice by'isi, bituma kiba ikibazo gikomeye ku buzima bw'abantu.
Mu buryo buhuje n'ubwoko bwa virusi ifitanye isano na yo, SARS-CoV, yateje abantu babarirwa mu bihumbi indwara ya SARS mu 2003, SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kuba yaraturutse ku birondwe kandi ikaba ifite ibimenyetso nk'ibyo kandi ikandura mu buryo bumwe.
Icyakora, COVID-19 ifite ubukana buke kandi ntiyica nk'iyo SARS ifite, ariko ikwirakwira cyane kandi yibasira abantu bakuze kurusha abakiri bato kandi yibasira cyane abagabo kurusha abagore.
Kubera ko ibitabo bivuga kuri iyi ndwara bikomeje kwiyongera, intego y'iyi nkuru ni ukugeza ku bantu amakuru ajyanye n'igihe n'ibikorwa by'ubushakashatsi bizakorwa kuri iyi ngingo.
Tuzasuzuma ibintu by'ingenzi birebana n'indwara, impamvu zitera iyo ndwara, uko umuntu ayirwara, uko ayirwara, uko ayirwara, uko ayirwara n'uko ayirinda.
Nubwo hari ibibazo byinshi bitarasubizwa, twizeye ko iyi ngingo izagufasha gusobanukirwa no guhangana n'iyo ndwara iteye ubwoba.
Ibirori byo kwizihiza umwaka wa 2020 ku itariki ya 25 Mutarama 2020 byabaye umwihariko kandi byibukwa n'Abashinwa bose, kuko abantu bose bari mu ngo bari barashyizwe mu kato mu gihe cyose cy'ibirori ndetse no mu byumweru byakurikiyeho kubera icyorezo gishya.
Iyi virusi ifite aho ihuriye na koronavirusi (CoV) yari icyorezo cy'indwara y'ubuhumekero ikaze (SARS) mu 2003; yaje kwitwa SARS-CoV-2 n'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ku ya 11 Gashyantare 2020, kandi indwara yateje yitwa CoV Disease-19 (COVID-19).
Iki cyorezo cy'indwara y'ibicurane cyatangiriye mu mujyi wa Wuhan mu Bushinwa, maze gikwirakwira mu Bushinwa hose ndetse no mu bihugu bigera kuri 50 ku isi.
Kugeza ku ya 2 Werurwe 2020, virusi yatumye abantu barenga 80.000 banduye COVID-19, abarenga 40.000 barakira, bararekurwa n'abarenga 3.000 barapfa.
OMS igabisha ko COVID-19 ari "umwanzi wa mbere ku isi" kandi ko ishobora kuba mbi kurusha iterabwoba.
Nk'uko bivugwa na PubMed (https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/), mu gihe kitarenze amezi abiri, abagore banditse inyandiko zirenga 200 zivuga kuri COVID-19 zirimo ibijyanye na virusi, icyorezo, impamvu, uburyo bwo kuyisuzuma n'uburyo bwo kuyirwanya, kuva raporo ya mbere yasohotse ku ya 7 Mutarama 2020 igaragaza uko virusi ikwirakwira mu bantu benshi.
Iyi ngingo igamije gusobanura muri make ubushakashatsi buzakorwa kuri icyo kintu gishya gikwirakwira mu buryo bwihuse.
Niba bishoboka, tugerageza kugereranya COVID-19 na SARS n'indi ndwara iterwa na CoV, indwara y'ibihaha yo mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati (MERS, yasohotse mu 2012).
Nanone turi busuzume ibyo tumaze kumenya ku birebana n'uko umuntu yarwanya iyo ndwara n'uko ayirwara, hamwe n'ibindi bibazo by'ingenzi.
Bivugwa ko CoVs ari indwara idasanzwe, akenshi ikaba itera ibicurane ku kigero cya 15%.
Ariko muri iki kinyejana, twabonye virusi z'ubwoko bubiri zandura abantu, urugero nka SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV, zatumye indwara zitangira gutandukana mu Bushinwa mu 2003 na Arabiya Sawudite mu 2012, kandi zikwirakwira mu bindi bihugu mu buryo bwihuse, zigira ingaruka ku bantu benshi kandi zikanahitana abantu benshi.
Ku bw'ibyo, COVID-19 iriho ubu ni yo CoV ya gatatu mu zindi zose zigeze kubaho.
Nk'uko bigaragara ku ishusho. Icyorezo cy'indwara y'ubuhumekero idasanzwe yo mu bwoko bwa 1.1, cyatangajwe bwa mbere i Wuhan ku ya 31 Gashyantare 2019 n'Ikigo cy'Igihugu cy'Ubuzima cy'u Bushinwa.
Nyuma y'iminsi irindwi, uburyo bwo gutangiza CoV bwarasohotse.
Ku ya 15 Mutarama 2020, umuntu wa mbere wapfuye muri Wuhan.
Icyo gihe, iyo ndwara yakwirakwiraga mu migi, mu turere no mu bihugu byo hafi aho.
Ku munsi wa 20, abaganga batangaje ko basanze iyo ndwara ishobora kwandura.
