Ibintu bitatu by'ingenzi by'ibanze bishobora gutuma umuntu yandura COVID-19 ni igitsina (umugabo), imyaka (≥60), no guhumeka nabi.
CoVs ni imwe mu nzego z'umuryango w'indwara z'ibyorezo kandi ni imwe mu ndwara zifite ubukana bwa RNA.
Iyi virusi ishobora gutandukanywa mu byiciro bine, urugero nka alpha, beta, gamma na delta, bityo alpha- na beta-CoVs bizwiho kwanduza abantu.
Imyunyuro ya (S) glycoprotein ifata ku miterere ya angiotensin ikora enzymes 2 (ACE2) na dipeptidyl peptidase 4 (DPP4) ya SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV, hanyuma ikora ku mubyimba.
RNA ya virusi ivumburwa mu cytoplasma; nyuma yo gukwirakwira, RNA ya virusi yinjira mu gice cy'urusobe rwa glycoprotein na nucleocapsid bigakora uduhimba tw'imyanya y'ubuhumekero tugizwe na virion, tugahura na plasma kugira ngo twubake virusi.
Genocide ya mbere ya SARS-CoV-2 yagaragaye ku itariki ya 10 Mutarama 2020.
SARS-CoV-2 yagaragaye ko ari beta-CoV nshya ifite ibimenyetso by'ubwirinzi ku rugero rwa 99,98% mu bipimo 10 byafashwe aho byatangiriye kugaragara, ku isoko ry'ibinyabuzima byo mu nyanja rya Huanan mu mujyi wa Wuhan.
SARS-CoV-2 ifite aho ihuriye na SARS-CoV ariko si na MERS-CoV.
Binyuze mu isanzuramuco ry'ikoranabuhanga, ibice bya SARS-CoV-2 bishobora kugaragara mu mubiri w'umuntu binyuze mu mwuka.
Icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2 cyateje ikibazo gikomeye mu bantu.
Icyakora, poroteyine S ya SARS-CoV-2 ntiyihuza cyane na ACE2 y'abantu kurusha SARS-CoV, ibyo bikaba bihuje n'uko SARS-CoV-2 idashobora gutera indwara zikomeye nk'iza SARS-CoV.
SARS-CoV-2 ishobora no gukora poroteyine nshya ntoya ya orf3b igakurura poroteyine ya orf8.
Impamvu ya mbere ni uko SARS-CoV-2 ifite ubwandu bw'ibice bibiri by'umubiri, kimwe cya kabiri cy'umubiri n'ibindi.
Ku ya 18 Gashyantare 2020, Zhou na bagenzi be, bavuze ko umubiri wa ACE2 wa cryo-EM w'abantu barebare cyane ufite 2,9 Å z'uruvange rw'ibintu bifite amino acide B0AT1.
Basanze izo ngiga zishobora gufunguka no gufunga, ziteranyirizwa hamwe, bityo ACE2-B0AT1 zisanzwe zishobora guhuza poroteyine ebyiri za S, zigatanga ibimenyetso byerekana ko CoV ifite ubukana.
B0AT1 ishobora kuba umuti w'indwara ya SARS-CoV-2.
