SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV bizwi ko byakomotse ku birondwe kandi ko byanduye abantu binyuze mu binyugunyugu bya civet na za ngamiya.
Iyo ugereranyije SARS-CoV-2 n'izindi virusi zanduye, abantu ni bo banduye SARS-CoV-2 mu birura kuko iyi virusi nshya ifite ubushobozi bwo guhura na 96% na virusi zanduye zo mu birura, aho SARS ebyiri zaturutse mu birura ari zo SL-CoVZX45 na SL-CoVZX21.
Ariko, uburyo bw'ingenzi bwatumye virusi iva mu matungo igera ku bantu ntiburamenyekana, kandi ntituramenya inzira y'inyamaswa.
Ji na bagenzi be bavuze ko inzoka ari zo zanyujije iyo virusi mu bantu ziyivanye mu birura, maze ikinjira muri poroteyine ya S.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe n'abashakashatsi bo mu mujyi wa Guangzhou mu Bushinwa, bwagaragaje ko ingona - inyamaswa zo mu bwoko bw'ibinyamanswa zikunze gukoreshwa mu buvuzi bw'ibyatsi mu Bushinwa - zishobora kuba ari zo zindi SARS-CoV-2 ikoresha mu gihe hari 99% by'amaraso y'ingona z'ubwoko bumwe na CoV zigaragara mu ngona no muri SARS-CoV-2.
Ariko kandi, itandukaniro ry'ibice 1% ku mikorobe zombi ni ryo ritandukanye cyane; bityo, tuzakomeza gutegereza umwanzuro uhamye (Ibisubizo).
Imikorere ya SARS-CoV-2 mu by'umubiri n'ibinyabuzima ntiharamenyekana neza.
SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV zishobora kubaho hanze y'aho zibarizwa mu gihe cy'amasaha 48 mu gihe cy'ubukonje bukabije, ndetse n'iminsi 5 mu gihe cy'ubushyuhe buri munsi ya 20 °C na 40%-50% mu gihe cy'ubukonje.
SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kugira imiterere nk'iyo.
Abantu bavuga ko SARS-CoV-2 idashobora guhangana n'imirasire y'urusobe rw'izuba n'ubushyuhe bwa dogere 56 mu gihe cy'iminota 30; cyangwa se ko 75% ya etanol, umuti wica udukoko urimo chlorine, aside parasitique, chloroforme, n'indi miti yica udukoko, ariko atari chlorhexidine, ishobora kwica virusi mu buryo bwiza.
Abantu bose ntibagira abasirikare barwanya SARS-CoV-2, bityo bakaba bashobora kwandura iyi virusi nshya.
Kugeza ubu, nta bushakashatsi bufatika bwakozwe ku buryo bwo kurwanya SARS-CoV-2.
Ku bw'ibyo, dushobora kuvuga gusa ku bushakashatsi bwakozwe mbere ku zindi virusi z'ubwoko bumwe na bumwe, cyane cyane SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV (Ibishushanyo 4).
Akenshi, iyo virusi yanduye, imiterere y'umubiri w'umuntu igaragazwa n'uburyo bwo kumenya ibimenyetso (PRRs) birimo ubwoko bwa C bw'ibinyabiziga, ibimenyetso bya Toll-like (TLR), NOD-like (NLR), na RIG-I-like (RLR).
Binyuze mu nzira zitandukanye, virusi itera indwara, igatera ingirabuzimafatizo z'amaraso, kandi ikongeraho interferon-type I (IFNs) mu buryo bwihuse, ibi bikaba bigabanya ikwirakwira rya virusi kandi bigatuma habaho ibinyabutabire byihuta.
Icyakora, poroteyine N ya SARS-CoV ishobora gufasha virusi guhangana n'ingaruka z'ubudahangarwa bw'umubiri.
Mu myaka ya vuba aha, abasirikare b'umubiri bagiye barushaho kwifatanya mu kurwanya virusi.
Imyunyungugu ya T, harimo n'utugingo twa T twa CD4+ na CD8+ zigira uruhare rukomeye mu kurwanya indwara.
Ingirabuzimafatizo za CD4+ zituma ingirabuzimafatizo za B zitanga abanduye, naho CD8+ zituma ingirabuzimafatizo za T zihita zica ingirabuzimafatizo zanduye.
Ingirabuzimafatizo za T z'indwara z'ibyorezo zituma habaho uturemangingo twitwa cytokines dutuma habaho indwara z'ibyorezo.
Icyakora, CoV ishobora gutuma ingirabuzimafatizo za T zidakora neza mu gihe zidakora neza.
Imirimo yo kurwanya virusi ikorwa n'imikorere y'imyakura y'umubiri, urugero nka C3a na C5a hamwe n'imikorere y'umubiri w'umubiri, na byo ni ingenzi mu kurwanya iyi virusi.
Urugero, abasirikare barwanya virusi bakurwa mu bantu bakize, bashobora kwica MERS-CoV.
Ariko kandi, iyo abashinzwe kurwanya indwara bakoze ibintu byinshi cyane, bishobora gutuma umubiri urushaho kugira ibyago byo kwandura indwara z'ibyorezo, bigatuma ibihaha byangirika, ingingo z'umubiri zikangirika, ndetse n'izindi ngingo zikangirika, ndetse n'umubiri ukabura imbaraga, ndetse n'ubuzima bukaba buhagaze.
SARS-CoV-2 , indwara yanduza mu buryo bw'ibanze, yibasira cyane abantu bakuze bafite izindi ndwara n'abagore batwite.
Abantu bafite virusi nyinshi cyangwa bafite ubwirinzi buke mu mubiri, akenshi barwara cyane kurusha abandi.
Igihe cyo kugaragaza SARS-CoV-2 ni iminsi 1-14 mu gihe cy'ibyumweru 3-7 bitewe n'ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku bantu 425 ba mbere banduye muri Wuhan.
