Ubusanzwe umuriro ni cyo kimenyetso cy'ingenzi kandi cya mbere cya COVID-19, gishobora kugaragara mu buryo bw'umwihariko cyangwa mu bindi bimenyetso nk'umusonga ukaze, guhumeka nabi, ububabare bw'imitsi, isesemi, kubabara mu muhogo, kubabara mu muhogo, guhumeka mu mazuru, ububabare mu gatuza, iseseme, kumva ushaka gusubiramo, no gucibwamwo.
Bamwe mu barwayi bagira ububabare bwo guhumeka n'/cyangwa guhumeka nabi mu gihe cy'icyumweru kimwe nyuma yo gutangira uburwayi.
Mu gihe indwara iba ikomeye cyane, abarwayi bahita bagira ibibazo byo guhumeka, umutima ugatera cyane, amaraso atemba cyane, kandi bagatera imbere.
Abantu bafite umuriro n'/cyangwa guhumeka nabi hamwe n'umuriro ukabije, ndetse n'abafite ikibazo cy'ibihaha, bagomba kugenzurwa.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku bantu bake mu mpera z'Ukuboza 2019 bwagaragaje ibimenyetso by'indwara ku bantu 98% bafite umuriro, 76% bafite ikimwaro, 55% bafite umwijima na 3% bafite iseseme; 8% bari bakeneye umwuka.
Ibisubizo bisa n'ibyo byavuye mu bushakashatsi bushya bwakozwe ku bantu babiri batanduye kandi batanduye.
Icyakora, ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu mwaka wa 2012 bwagaragaje ko abantu benshi barwaye MERS-CoV bagaragazaga umuriro (98%), inkorora ikomeye (47%), no guhumeka nabi (55%).
Ariko 80% by'abo bantu bari bakeneye ubufasha bwo mu kirere, ni ukuvuga umubare munini w'abarwaye COVID-19 kandi bahitanwa na MERS ugereranyije na COVID-19.
Guhekenya cyane (26%) no kubabara mu muhogo (21%) na byo byagaragaraga mu barwayi ba MERS.
Mu barwayi ba SARS, basanze umuriro (99%-100%), inkorora ikomeye (29%-75%), iseseme (40%-42%), iseseme (20-25%), no kubabara mu muhogo (13-25%) ari ibimenyetso by'ingenzi kandi hafi 14%-20% by'abarwayi bakeneraga umwuka.
Ku ya 14 Gashyantare, umubare w'abamaze guhitanwa na COVID-19 wari 2% mu gihe umubare w'abamaze guhitanwa n'iki cyorezo wari 66,576.
