Kugereranya SARS-CoV-2 na MERS-CoV na SARA-CoV mu bijyanye n'ibimenyetso, ubwandu, n'umubare wa R0 byerekanwe mu mbonerahamwe.
Ibipimo biri hejuru bigaragaza ko SARS-CoV-2 ifite ubushobozi bwo kwandura cyane kurusha MERS-CoV na SARS-CoV, ariko ko ihitana abantu bake ugereranyije n'izo zindi ebyiri.
Ku bw'ibyo, indwara zandura za SARS-CoV-2 zirushaho kugorana kuzirwanya ugereranyije n'izandura za MERS-CoV na SARS-CoV.
Akenshi, ibyo bikoresho bituruka mu muryango cyangwa ahantu runaka cyangwa bikaza mu bwato.
Abanduye ni abantu basanzwe bagiye cyangwa baba mu duce cyangwa ahantu hatangiriye icyorezo cyangwa bakandamijwe n'abantu mu byumweru bibiri bya mbere y'uko kigaragara.
Icyakora, birashoboka ko abantu bashobora kwandura virusi nta bimenyetso bagaragaza mu gihe kirenze ibyumweru bibiri, kandi abantu bakize bakongera kwandura iyo virusi nyuma yo kuva mu bitaro, bityo igihe cyo gushyirwa mu kato kigomba kongerwa.
Abarwayi bafite umubare muto cyangwa usanzwe w'utugingo tw'amaraso yera (cyane cyane utw'utugingo tw'amaraso) mu gihe cy'indwara.
Urugero, indwara y'impuzandengo y'amaraso ifite umubare w'utugingo tw'amaraso twera &lt; 4×109/L hamwe n'umubare w'utugingo tw'amaraso &lt; 1×109/L, hamwe n'umubare munini wa aspartate aminotransferase na viremia byagaragaye mu barwayi 1 099 banduye COVID-19.
Hari abarwayi bagaragaje ko amaraso yabo afite za enzymes zo mu maraso n'izindi nzego z'umubiri, kandi abenshi muri bo bari bafite poroteyine C n'utundi duce duto cyane tw'amaraso.
Mu barwayi barembye cyane, urugero rw'umusemburo witwa dimer D, ari na rwo rugaragaza ko hari udutsi tw'amaraso twongera gukora nabi, maze utwo dusemburo tukagenda tugabanuka.
Ibibazo byo mu gatuza byagaragariye ku bantu benshi banduye COVID-19 kandi bagaragazaga ibihuha bitandukanye cyangwa ibihuha mu bihaha.
Abarwayi bakunze kugira indwara z'ubuhumekero, ibikomere bikomeye by'ibihaha n'indwara y'ubuhumekero idakira (ARDS).
Iyo indwara ya ARDS ibayeho, ububabare bukabije, amazi menshi mu mubiri no kwangirika kw'imyanya y'umubiri bituma guhumeka biba bigoye.
Imikorere mibi y'utugingo tw'amaraso two mu bwoko bwa I na II ituma habaho kugabanuka kw'imikorere y'utugingo tw'amaraso kandi bigatuma habaho imiterere y'uruhande rw'amaraso, bityo bigatuma ibihaha bidakora neza kandi bigatuma ibyago byo kwandura mu bihaha byiyongera.
Ibyo byatumye indwara ikomeye y'ibihaha akenshi iba ifitanye isano n'imibabaro ikomeye.
Ku ya 18 Gashyantare 2020, isuzuma rya mbere rya COVID-19 ryagaragaje ko hari ibisebe by'ibihaha byangiritse, ibice bya hyaline, no gusenyuka kwa za limfocyte zo mu nda, hamwe n'udutsi tw'amasohoro mu masohoro y'ibihaha by'abantu bapfuye, bihuye n'indwara ya virusi na ARDS kandi bisa n'ibisanzwe mu bantu barwaye SARS na MERS.
Kumenya RNA ya SARS-CoV-2 binyuze mu ikoranabuhanga ry'ikoranabuhanga (RT-PCR) byakoreshejwe nk'ikimenyetso cy'ingenzi mu gupima COVID-19.
Icyakora, kubera ko amakuru atari yo akwirakwizwa cyane, ashobora gutuma icyorezo kirushaho kwiyongera, icyorezo cyatangiye kwemezwa hakoreshejwe ibimenyetso (bitarimo RT-PCR gusa) mu Bushinwa ku ya 13 Gashyantare 2020.
Ibintu nk'ibyo byagiye bikorwa mu gusuzuma indwara ya SARS.
Ni yo mpamvu, guhuza amateka y'uburwayi, uko bwagenze, ibipimo bya laboratwari, hamwe n'ibisubizo bya radiographie ari ingenzi kandi bifasha mu kumenya neza icyorezo.
Ku ya 14 Gashyantare 2020, itsinda rya Feng Zhang ryasobanuye uburyo bwo gupima hakoreshejwe uburyo bushingiye kuri CRISPR SHERLOCK bwo gupima SARS-CoV-2, bwo gupima SARS-CoV-2 RNA mu gipimo cya 20 × 10-18 mol/L cyangwa 200 × 10-18 mol/L (umubare 10-100 muri microlitiro) hakoreshejwe ibipimo mu gihe kitarenze isaha nta ngamba z'urudaca.
Turizera ko ubu buryo bushya bushobora guhindura cyane uburyo bwo kumva no gukoresha, niba bwemejwe nyuma yo gusuzumwa.
Kubera ko nta bumenyi buhagije buhari ku ndwara ya koronavirusi nshya, abaganga bashobora kuvura gusa mu rugero ruciriritse abarwayi ba COVID-19, mu gihe hagitegerejwe imiti myinshi ikoreshwa cyangwa yatekerejwe mbere yo kuvura abantu bafite izindi ndwara za koronavirusi, urugero nka SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV hamwe n'indwara ziterwa na virusi (Imbonerahamwe (Imbonerahamwe2).2).
Izo miti ni imiti mishya kandi ishobora gukoreshwa irimo imiti y'imbuto, imiti igabanya ubudahangarwa bw'umubiri, siteroyi, plasma y'umurwayi, imiti gakondo y'Abashinwa, n'imiti y'ubuvuzi.
Hari n'abavuze ko bashobora gukoresha amaraso y'umurwayi mu buryo bw'ubuvuzi.
Amashyirahamwe y'ubuvuzi azakora uko ashoboye kugira ngo avumbure imiti n'inkingo bya virusi.
SARS-CoV-2 yibasira cyane cyane ibihaha mu gihe cy'imikurire, kandi rimwe na rimwe ikagira ingaruka ku bindi bice by'umubiri bifite ACE2, urugero nk'igifu n'impyiko.
Nyamara, guhumeka nabi no kubura ubwenge ni ibintu biteje akaga cyane ku barwayi benshi kandi ni byo bituma abantu benshi bapfa.
Ku bw'ibyo, ubufasha bwo guhumeka ni ingenzi mu kugabanya ibimenyetso no gukiza indwara, kandi bukubiyemo gutanga umwuka wa ogisijeni mu buryo bw'imiti, gutanga umwuka wa ogisijeni mu rugero rwagutse, guhumeka neza no gutera umwuka mu mubiri ukurikije ubukana bw'indwara.
Abarwayi bafite ibibazo bikomeye byo guhumeka, bafashwa n'uburyo bushya bwo gutera umwuka mu mubiri (ECMO), uburyo bushya bwo gutera umutima mu mubiri bukoreshwa mu kuvura indwara ikomeye y'umutima cyangwa guhumeka nabi.
Byongeye kandi, kubungabunga ubusumbane bwa electrolyte, kurwanya no kuvura indwara z'ibyorezo n'indwara zikomeye, no kubungabunga ubuzima bw'umubiri ni ingenzi ku bantu banduye SARS-CoV-2.
Byemezwa ko kwiyongera kwa sitokine mu mubiri bigendana no kurwara cyane mu bantu barwaye SARS na MERS.
Cytokine ni ubwoko bw'indwara ziterwa n'indwara ziterwa n'indwara ziterwa n'indwara zitandukanye, urugero nka TNFα, IL-1β, IL-2, IL-6, IFNα, IFNβ, IFNγ, na MCP-1.
Cytokines zituma ingirabuzimafatizo z'umubiri zisohora ibintu byinshi bitandukanye bituma indwara ya ARDS n'ibindi bice by'umubiri byangiza.
Immunosuppresseur ni ingenzi mu kuvura cytokines, cyane cyane mu barwayi barembye.
Imiti yitwa corticosteroid na tocilizumab, ni ukuvuga umuti urwanya indwara witwa IL6, yakoreshejwe mu kuvura indwara ziterwa n'imyakura.
Hari imiti imwe n'imwe ihagarika ubudahangarwa bw'umubiri ikoresha uturemangingo twa T dufasha mu kurwanya indwara; ifunga IFN-γ, IL-1, na TNF; ihagarika JAK; blinatumomabe; ihagarika uburyo bwo kugaragaza uturemangingo twa 4 twa cytocine; n'ihagarika HDAC.
Steroids, nk'imiti igabanya ubukana bw'umubiri, zakoreshejwe cyane mu kuvura SARS mu kugabanya ububabare.
Icyakora, gukoresha ibipimo byinshi bya siteroide ntibyari ngombwa mu kuvura ibikomere byo mu bihaha mu barwayi ba SARS na COVID-19.
Ariko kandi, bishobora guteza ibibazo, cyane cyane mu maraso, kandi bigatuma umuntu atabona ibisubizo by'ibibazo afite.
Icyakora, ingano yo hasi ya corticosteroid yasabwe ko itangwa mu buryo bwitondewe ku barwayi ba COVID-19 barwaye cyane.
Mu gihe twandika, nta muti uzwi kuri iyi virusi uraboneka.
Icyakora, gutera intanga ya remdesivir, analogue ya nucleotide, byagaragaye ko ari ingirakamaro cyane mu bantu bo muri Amerika barwaye COVID-19.
Remdesivir ni umuti urwanya virusi watangijwe na Gilead mu kuvura abarwayi ba Ebola na Marlburg.
Nyuma yaho, imiti ya remdesivir yagaragaje ko ishobora kuvura izindi virusi ziterwa na RNA harimo MERS na SARS.
Mu gihe ibyo byemezwa, Gilead yatanze ibikoresho mu Bushinwa kugira ngo bikoreshwe mu gupima abantu banduye SARS-CoV-2, kandi abantu bategereje cyane ibisubizo.
Byongeye kandi, hari amakuru avuga ko baricitinbe, interferone-α, lopinavir/ritonavir, na ribavirin, bishobora gufasha abantu bafite ibibazo bikomeye byo guhumeka.
Isesemi, gusonza, gucibwamwo, kwangirika kw'umwijima, n'ibindi bibazo bishobora kubaho iyo imiti ifatanywe na lopinavir/ritonavir.
