Abagore bagerageje urukingo rw'indwara ya SARS mu matungo.
Ariko kandi, nta kimenyetso gifatika cy'uko urukingo rushobora kugira ingaruka nziza ku bantu bageze mu za bukuru n'abarwaye indwara zikomeye, ndetse n'uko rukingira abantu virusi z'inyamaswa, kugeza ubwo hakorwa ubushakashatsi ku bantu.
Ibi bishobora kuba biterwa n'uko SARS imaze imyaka 17 kandi nta muntu n'umwe wongeye kwandura kuva icyo gihe.
