Dukurikije ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku bagore, ibintu bikurikira bishobora kugira ingaruka cyangwa bifitanye isano n'imiterere y'ubwandu bwa COVID-19 (Imbonerahamwe (Imbonerahamwe33)):
Imvura: Imvura ni ikintu cy'ingenzi mu kugaragaza uko SARS iteye, kandi ni na ko bimeze kuri COVID-19.
COVID-19 yibasiye cyane cyane abantu bafite imyaka iri hagati ya 30 na 65 kuko 47,7% by'abarwayi bari bafite imyaka iri hejuru ya 50 mu bushakashatsi bwakozwe ku bantu 8,866 nk'uko byasobanuwe haruguru.
Abarwayi bari mu bitaro byita ku barwayi barwaye cyane bagaragaje ibimenyetso bimwe na bimwe bibi n'ububabare kandi barembye kurusha abatarwaye (imyaka 66 na 51), ibyo bikaba bigaragaza ko imyaka ari kimwe mu bintu by'ingenzi bigena uko umuntu uzarwara COVID-19 azakira.
