Indwara y'umutima ni yo mpamvu nyamukuru y'urupfu mu barwayi ba SARS.
Bivugwa ko SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kuba ifite aho ihuriye na ACE2 cholangiocytes, ishobora gutuma impyiko zidakora neza mu barwayi ba COVID-19.
