Impamvu z'imiterere y'ubudahangarwa bwa CRP n'uburwayi bwa COVID-19 na zo zagiye zigeragezwa.
Byongeye kandi, urugero rwo hejuru rwa lactate dehydrogenase (LDH), aspartate aminotransferase (AST), alanine aminotransferase (ALT), na creatine kinase (CK) bishobora kugira uruhare mu kumenya niba umuntu azakira cyangwa atazarokoka.
Izo poroteyine z'umwuka zituruka mu ngingo nyinshi z'umubiri, cyane cyane mu mutima no mu kibyimba, kandi zisohoka iyo hari ingingo z'umubiri zangijwe.
