Turamutse tutabonye ibisubizo by'ibyo bibazo, ntidushobora kumenya uburyo bwiza bwo kwivuza.
Ese iyo ndwara izamara igihe kingana iki?
Ni gute virusi ikwirakwira mu maraso mu mubiri w'umuntu?
Ese izaba icyorezo ku isi, izarangira burundu nka SARS cyangwa izajya ivuka kenshi nka grippe?
Ni ngombwa ariko bishobora gufata igihe kirekire kugira ngo umuntu abone ibisubizo by'ibyo bibazo ndetse n'ibindi byinshi.
Ariko, uko ibyo bishobora kutugora kose, icyo tugomba gukora ni ukugabanya icyorezo vuba na bwangu, maze ubuzima bwacu bukongera kuba nk'uko bwari bumeze mbere.
Koronavirusi y'abantu yakomotse ku nyamaswa
Imiterere y'ubwoko n'imiterere y'ubwoko bw'indwara zitera indwara (CoVs) n'ibikoresho by'ubwoko bwazo, harimo n'abantu, bishobora kubaho mu gihe cy'imyaka myinshi.
Mbere y'umwaka wa 2003, abantu babiri muri bo bari bazwiho kuba bafite virusi z'ubwoko bwa CoV (HCoVs) zitatera indwara zikomeye, urugero nk'ibicurane.
Icyorezo cya SARS n'icyorezo cy'indwara y'ubuhumekero yo mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati (MERS) byerekana ko HCoV ishobora kwanduza abantu kandi ikabica.
Icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2 mu Bushinwa bwo hagati mu mpera za 2019 cyatumye CoVs ziza ku isonga kandi byadutangaje kubera ko zakwirakwiriye cyane ariko zikaba zitanduye cyane kurusha SARS-CoV.
Iyo virusi ishobora kwandura mu buryo bw'impanuka, ariko iyo itangiye kwandura mu buryo bw'impanuka, ishobora no kwandura mu buryo bw'impanuka.
Impamvu imwe ni uko hari abantu benshi batanduye HCoVs, ariko hari n'abandi benshi batanduye.
Hari kandi n'izindi virusi z'ubwoko bumwe na bumwe zitwara virusi z'ubwoko bumwe na bumwe.
Kumenya inyamaswa zitwara indwara ni ingenzi mu kurwanya indwara zandura abantu.
Gushakisha isano iri hagati y'ubwoko bw'indwara za CoV mu nyamaswa na byo bishobora gufasha cyane mu kumenya indwara za CoV mu bantu.
Muri iyi ngingo, tugiye gusubiramo muri make ibyo tuzi ku ndwara zirindwi za HCoVs, twibanda ku mateka y'ubushakashatsi bwazo n'imiterere yazo mu nyamaswa n'ibinyabuzima by'inyamaswa.
Mu buryo bw'ibanze, dushobora kugereranya no gutandukanya HCoVs nyinshi dushingiye ku buryo virusi ikura n'uburyo genome ihurizwa hamwe.
Icyorezo cya CoV cya 2019 (COVID-19) cyasobanuwe muri iyi ngingo.
Ikindi kandi, igaragaza ibyo umuntu akenera kugira ngo ahindure mu buryo bugira ingaruka ibintu bituma indwara ziterwa n'ubwandu n'uko virusi ikomeza kwiyongera no gukomera.
Koronavirusi (CoVs) ni zo zigize umuryango wa Coronaviridae, ugizwe n'itsinda ry'indwara ziterwa na virusi z'umushongi wa RNA.
Virusi zifite genome nini iri hagati ya kilobases 26 na 32 muri virusi za RNA, zitiriwe CoVs kubera ko zari zifite umwenda w'ingofero kuri mikorosikopi ya elegitoroniki.
Mu mubiri, CoVs ntizigira ibinyabuzima by'ubwoko bumwe.
Hafi bibiri bya gatatu bya jenome bifite ibice bibiri by'ingenzi by'ingenzi (ORF1a na ORF1b), bihindurwamo poroteyine zigena pp1 na pp1ab.
Nanone, izo poroteyine nyinshi zikoreshwa mu gukora za poroteyine 16 z'ingirabuzimafatizo, zitwa nsp1~16.
Ibisigaye bya jenome birimo ORFs zigereranya imiterere ya poroteyine, harimo uruhu (S), uruhu (E), uruhu (M) na nucleoproteins (N).
Hari poroteyine zimwe na zimwe zinyuranye zanditse mu buryo butandukanye bwa CoV.
Ku bijyanye n'ubwoko bw'indwara ya HCoVs, hari ibimenyetso byinshi bigaragaza ko iyi virusi ishobora kwandura mu buryo butandukanye, ariko hari ibimenyetso byinshi bigaragaza ko ishobora kwandura mu buryo butandukanye.
Ibihamya by'imiterere y'ingirabuzima fatizo bigaragaza ko udusimba n'imbeba ari byo byibanda ku bwoko bw'ingirabuzima fatizo za alpha-CoVs na beta-CoVs, ariko inyoni ni zo ahanini ziturukaho za gamma-CoVs na delta-CoVs.
Mu myaka ibarirwa mu bihumbi, CoVs zakunze guhura n'abantu mu buryo butandukanye, kandi zimwe muri zo zahindutse virusi z'ubwoko bwa kimuntu.
Kugeza ubu, hamaze kumenyekana ubwoko burindwi bwa virusi z'ubwoko bw'abantu (HCoVs).
Muri izo, HCoV-229E na HCoV-NL63 ni alpha-CoVs.
Icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2 cyateje ikibazo gikomeye mu bantu benshi, kuko cyageze no ku bantu benshi cyane.
Iyo umuntu afite ibimenyetso by'indwara ya HCoV-229E, HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1 na HCoV-NL63, akenshi aba afite ibimenyetso byoroheje, urugero nk'ubukonje n'indwara y'igifu.
Mu buryo bunyuranye n'ubwo, SARS-CoV, MERS-CoV na SARS-CoV-2 z'ubu ni zo zidakira cyane, zangiza cyane imyanya y'ubuhumekero yo hasi mu barwayi benshi bafite ibyago byinshi byo kurwara indwara z'ubuhumekero ziterwa n'ihungabana (ARDS) n'izindi ndwara z'ibihaha.
Impamvu ya mbere y'ubwandu bwa HCoV-229E, B814, yagaragaye mu myuzure y'abantu barwaye ibicurane mu myaka ya za 1960.
Kuva icyo gihe, ubushakashatsi bwinshi bwakozwe bwatumye habaho ubushakashatsi ku burwayi bwa HCoV-229E na HCoV-OC43, byombi bikaba bitera ibimenyetso bike.
Mu by'ukuri, kugeza igihe SARS yadutse, abantu benshi bemeraga igitekerezo cy'uko HCoVs nta ngaruka mbi zigira.
Icyorezo cya SARS cyo mu mwaka wa 2003 ni kimwe mu byorezo by'indwara z'ibyorezo bikomeye mu bihe bya none, cyishe abantu barenga 8.000 kandi gihitana hafi 10% by'abanduye.
Mu myaka icumi, indwara y'ibicurane byo mu burasirazuba bwo hagati (MERS) yabaye icyorezo mu karere ka Arabiya, kandi ikwirakwira hirya no hino ku isi.
Icyorezo cya HCoV (2019-nCoV) cyo mu mwaka wa 2019, cyiswe SARS-CoV-2, ni cyo cyateje icyorezo cya coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19), kimaze guhitana abantu barenga 3 120 n'abarenga 91 000 kugeza ku itariki ya 3 Werurwe 2020.
Hariho imiburo iteganyijwe kandi isi yose iri mu myiteguro yo guhangana n'icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2.
Iyi virusi ya mbere ya SARS-CoV-2 ni imwe mu zanduye abantu benshi cyane, ariko mu by'ukuri nta n'umwe muri bo wanduye iyi virusi.
Ibipimo byerekana ko HCoVs zose zituruka mu birura, aho virusi ikunda kuba kandi ntiyihindure ariko ikagira amoko menshi.
Icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyagize ingaruka zikomeye ku buvuzi, ku bahanga mu bya siyansi, ku mibereho n'umuco by'Abashinwa no ku isi yose.
Gukurikirana aho HCoVs zakomotse mu nyamaswa bituma tumenya amateka y'imiterere, imbaraga z'ubuyobozi n'ibibuza inyamaswa kuguruka.
Ibi bishobora kandi kuyobora cyangwa gufasha mu bushakashatsi ku mibereho, ubwandu n'imiterere y'ibinyabuzima bitera SARS-CoV-2, ndetse no mu bikorwa byo kwirinda ikwirakwira ryayo mu gihe kizaza.
Muri iyi ngingo, turi busuzume muri make inkomoko y'izo virusi, uko zikwirakwizwa n'ibindi biremwa n'uko virusi za HCoV zikwirakwizwa.
Mu buryo bwihariye, tuvuga kandi tuvuga ku kintu cy'ingenzi cyane, ni ukuvuga ko virusi z'ingenzi za HCoVs zitatera indwara mu gace zibamo, ahubwo ko zitera indwara iyo zivuye mu bwoko bumwe zigasubira mu kandi.
Nanone kandi, twasuzumye uko HCoV ikura n'ukuntu akenshi iyo igeze mu bindi binyabuzima, ituma idashobora kwanduza abantu benshi.
Ibi ni bimwe mu byaranze iyi ndwara ya SARS-CoV-2.
Indwara ya CoV mu nyamaswa zamenyekanye kuva mu mpera z'imyaka ya 1930.
Mbere y'uko ibimenyetso bya mbere bya HCoV-229E, B814, biboneka mu mwonga w'abantu barwaye ibicurane, CoVs zari zimaze kuboneka mu nyamaswa nyinshi, harimo inkende, imbeba, inka, ingurube, injangwe n'imbwa.
Mu myaka ishize, abantu bavumbuye HCoVs zirindwi.
Mu buryo bw'ibanze, iyi virusi ishobora kuba ifite ubumara butandukanye n'ubundi, ariko ikagira ubushobozi bwo guhangana n'ubwandu bw'izindi ndwara.
HCoV-229E yabonetse bwa mbere mu bwonko bw'abantu barwaye indwara y'ubuhumekero mu mwaka wa 1966, nyuma yaho ikura mu ngirabuzima fatizo z'ibicurane WI-38.
Abarwayi banduye HCoV-229E bagaragaje ibimenyetso byinshi by'ibicurane birimo kubabara mu maso, mu maso, mu ngingo no mu muhogo hamwe n'umuriro n'ikoni byagaragariye mu bantu bari hagati ya 10 na 20%.
Nyuma yaho mu mwaka wa 1967, HCoV-OC43 yavumbuwe mu mico y'ingingo maze yimurirwa mu bwonko bw'imbeba.
Impamvu zituma abantu barwara indwara z'ibicurane ni uko hari ibimenyetso byinshi byerekana ko umuntu arwaye indwara z'ibicurane.
Iyo virusi ifite ubukana bukomeye cyane, ikagira ubukana budafite uko bungana n'ubw'izindi virusi z'ibyorezo.
Akenshi, iminsi mikuru y'ubwandu bw'indwara ebyiri z'ibyorezo iba mu cyumweru kimwe, hanyuma umuntu akarwara mu gihe cy'ibyumweru hafi bibiri.
Ibipimo byakozwe n'abaganga bivuga ko iyi virusi ishobora gutera indwara z'ibyorezo, ariko ko hari n'abandi bantu bafite uburwayi bw'ibicurane.
Abarwayi bake bafite ubuzima budafite imbaraga ni bo bagaragaweho indwara y'ubuhumekero idakira.
SARS, nanone izwi ku izina rya indwara y'ibihaha, ni HCoV yo mu bitabo by'ibanze by'ubushakashatsi yatumye haba icyorezo cya mbere mu mateka y'abantu kandi yakomotse kuri SARS-CoV, HCoV ya gatatu yavumbuwe n'abantu.
Umuntu wa mbere wanduye SARS ashobora kuba yarabonetse mu mwaka wa 2002 mu ntara ya Guangdong mu Bushinwa.
Icyorezo cya SARS cyateje abantu 8,096 n'abantu 774 bahitanywe na cyo, cyakwirakwiriye mu bihugu byinshi no ku migabane myinshi.
Uretse kuba hari ibintu byanduza, byaje kugaragara ko ubwandu bw'iyo ndwara bufata iminsi iri hagati ya ine n'irindwi, kandi ko igera ku bantu benshi ku munsi wa 10.
Abantu banduye SARS-CoV bagaragaza ibimenyetso by'ububabare mu mitsi, kubabara, umuriro, ibicurane n'imbeho, bikurikirwa no guhumeka nabi, inkorora n'ibibazo byo guhumeka.
Indwara ya SARS ikunze kugaragara cyane mu gihe cy'uburwayi, mu gihe indwara ya SARS ikomeje kwiyongera.
Kugabanya imikorere y'utugingo tw'amaraso, gukura vuba kw'utugingo tw'amaraso n'umubare munini w'utugingo tw'amaraso (macrophages) na byo bigaragara mu barwayi ba SARS.
Hafi ya 20-30% by'abarwayi bafatwa n'iyo ndwara bajya mu cyumba cy'indembe kandi bagakenera umwuka.
Ikindi kandi, mu gice cyo hasi cy'ubuhumekero, ingingo nyinshi, urugero nk'igifu, ibihaha n'impyiko, zishobora kwangirika mu gihe indwara ikomeye, akenshi bigatuma habaho imikorere y'imiti yitwa cytokines, ibyo bikaba bishobora no guhitana abantu bafite ubumuga.
Virusi yagaragaye bwa mbere mu isuzuma ry'umubiri ryakozwe ku murwayi wo mu muryango w'umurwayi wavuye i Guangzhou ajya muri Hong Kong.
Kuva icyo gihe, abantu bagiye bakora ubushakashatsi bwinshi ku ndwara ya HCoV.
HCoV-NL63 yanduye mu ruhinja rw'amezi arindwi rwo mu Buholandi mu mpera z'umwaka wa 2004.
Mbere yaho, byagaragaraga ko abantu benshi barwaye indwara z'ibicurane ari abakiri bato, abageze mu za bukuru n'abarwaye indwara zo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero.
Ibipimo by'ibicurane, indwara y'uruhu, umuriro mwinshi n'indwara z'ubuhumekero ni bimwe mu bimenyetso by'indwara ziterwa na HCoV-NL63.
Hari ubundi bushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko virusi yabonetse mu binure by'umwana w'amezi umunani wari urwaye rubagimpande mu Buholandi.
Nubwo icyo cyorezo cyavumbuwe mu Buholandi, cyahise kigera mu baturage bose.
HCoV-NL63 ishobora kuba itera indwara z'ubuhumekero zigera kuri 4,7%, kandi abantu benshi bayirwaye mu ntangiriro z'impeshyi, mu gihe cy'imvura no mu gihe cy'ubukonje bukabije.
HCoV-NL63 kandi ishobora gutera indwara y'ubuhumekero ifata imyanya y'ibere, izwi kandi ku izina rya croup.
Muri uwo mwaka, HCoV-HKU1 yanduye umugabo w'imyaka 71 wari waragiye mu bitaro kubera impiswi na bronchiolitis muri Hong Kong.
Uretse indwara y'ibihaha n'indwara y'ibihaha, HCoV-HKU1 ishobora no kuvugwaho kugira uruhare mu gutuma umuntu arwara ibicurane bikomeye.
Nk'uko byagenze kuri HCoV-NL63, HCoV-229E na HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1 yagaragaye ku isi hose, kandi yatumye abantu barwara indwara z'ubuhumekero.
HCoVs zose uko ari enye zisanzwe zihuza abantu kandi akenshi ntizikunda gutera indwara zikomeye cyane, nubwo impanuka zabayeho kubera impamvu zitazwi kandi hari ingero nke z'ubwoko bwa HCoV-NL63 zidakomeye cyane, ziherutse kuvugwa ko zitera indwara nke z'ubuhumekero mu Bushinwa.
Ubusanzwe, igihe HCoVs zishobora gukwirakwira neza hagati y'abantu kandi zikaguma mu mubiri, ntizikunda kugira imbaraga nyinshi cyangwa ngo zigire ubushobozi bwo kuvura.
MERS-CoV yagaragaye bwa mbere mu 2012 mu mwonko w'umurwayi w'imyaka 60 wari ufite ibibazo bikomeye by'ibihaha n'impyiko mu gihugu cya Arabie Saoudite.
Nubwo abenshi mu banduye bari baturutse mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati, icyorezo cyakwirakwiriye mu bindi bihugu binyuze mu guhura cyane n'ibihugu bitandukanye by'i Burayi na Tuniziya.
Mu mwaka wa 2015, muri Koreya y'Epfo habaye ikindi gikorwa gito cyo gutwara abantu mu ngendo, cyatwaye abantu 186.
Ibimenyetso bya MERS bisa n'ibya SARS, akenshi bigaragara mu gihe cy'indwara ikomeye y'ibihaha.
Mu buryo bunyuranye na SARS, abenshi mu banduye MERS na bo barwaye indwara ikomeye y'impyiko, itandukanye n'iyo muri izindi ndwara ziterwa na HCoV.
Abarwayi basaga 30 bagaragaje ibimenyetso by'indwara z'igifu, urugero nk'ihosha n'igisebe.
Ku ya 14 Gashyantare 2020, hari hamaze kumenyekana abantu barenga 2500 banduye iyi virusi, abagera kuri 34,4% muri bo bakaba barapfuye, bituma MERS-CoV iba imwe mu ndwara zangiza cyane.
Mu mpera z'Ukuboza 2019, abantu barwaye indwara y'ubuhumekero yari isanzwe izwiho kuba yaratewe na SARS-CoV-2 bagaragaye i Wuhan, mu Ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryemeje ko indwara y'ubuhumekero iterwa na SARS-CoV-2 ari ikibazo cy'ingorabahizi cyugarije isi yose, kandi ko ari COVID-19.
Ku ya 3 Werurwe 2020, abantu 90,053 ni bo bari baranduye ku isi hose, mu gihe umubare w'abapfuye wari 3,4%.
Igishishikaje ni uko muri Hubei, mu Bushinwa, umubare w'abapfuye ari 4,2 ku ijana, mu gihe hanze yaho ari 1,2 ku ijana.
SARS-CoV-2 ituma indwara z'ubuhumekero zikomeye, urugero nka SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV, zigaragazwa n'umuriro mwinshi, inkorora n'ubuhumekero bugoye.
Hari abandi barwayi na bo bari bafite ikibazo cy'umushonga.
Indwara y'ibihaha ni kimwe mu bimenyetso bikomeye kandi bishobora guhita bihinduka indwara ikomeye y'ubuhumekero.
Nubwo SARS-CoV na SARS-CoV-2 zifite aho zihuriye mu buryo bw'ibanze mu gukora ibice 82% by'uduporotayiti, zinyuranye mu bice byinshi no mu matsinda y'indwara.
SARS-CoV-2 igaragara ko idakomeye cyane ariko ikwirakwira cyane mu bantu iyo uyifashe nk'iyo SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV.
SARS-CoV-2 kandi yagaragaye mu bantu batagaragaza ibimenyetso kandi ishobora kuba yaratumye ikwirakwira ku isi hose mu buryo bwihuse.
Impamvu ya mbere ni uko SARS-CoV-2 ifite ubushobozi bwo guhangana n'izindi virusi esheshatu z'ubwoko bumwe, ariko ikagira n'ubushobozi bwo guhangana n'izindi.
Icya mbere, igihe indwara iba itangiye n'igihe iba irangiriye, birasa cyane.
Muri ubwo buryo, SARS-CoV-2 ifite ibintu byinshi ihuriyeho n'izindi HCoV esheshatu.
Icya kabiri, ibimenyetso bikomeye bya COVID-19 biboneka muri SARS-CoV na HCoVs enye zindi (urugero, HCoV-229E, HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1 na HCoV-NL63).
Mu bice bimwe na bimwe, SARS-CoV-2 igaragaza ibimenyetso bisanzwe bigaragara mu gihe cy'indwara z'ubwoko bwa HCoVs mu bantu, harimo no kugaragaza ibimenyetso bidasanzwe, bike cyangwa nta n'ibimenyetso.
Mu bindi bice, abantu bake barwaye COVID-19 ikomeye bashobora no kuba baranduye SARS-CoV, nubwo umubare wabo waba uri hasi.
Icya gatatu, ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2 bugaragaza ko hari ibintu bimwe na bimwe bisa n'ibiri mu miterere ya HCoVs mu bantu na SARS-CoV.
Ikindi kandi, ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2 ni bwinshi cyane ugereranyije na HCoVs mu bantu.
Mu rwego rwo kwirinda, hagomba gusuzumwa niba ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2 bugabanuka nyuma yo kwandura nk'uko byagenze kuri SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV.
Mu buryo nk'ubwo, SARS-CoV-2 ishobora no kugaragara mu myanda y'umuntu, nk'uko bimeze ku zindi HCoV.
Nubwo SARS-CoV-2 yandura abantu binyuze mu myanda, ni ingenzi cyane nk'uko byagenze kuri SARS-CoV, kandi hakenewe ubundi bushakashatsi buzakomeza mu gihe kiri imbere.
Mu buryo buhuje n'ibyo, abantu benshi bafite indwara ya SARS-CoV-2 bafite ibibazo by'uburwayi.
Icyakora, hari ibintu bimwe na bimwe bya SARS-CoV-2 n'uburyo bw'ubwandu, imiterere n'imikorere byayo nyuma yo kwinjira mu bantu bizagira ingaruka ku mwuka wa COVID-19.
Impamvu imwe ni uko hari abantu benshi batemera ko virusi ya koronavirusi ishobora kwandura.
Mu buryo bunyuranye n'ubwo, birashoboka ko abagore bamenyereye cyane izo HCoV uko ari enye.
Mu buryo bw'ikigereranyo, izo virusi zombi zishobora kuba zaragize ingaruka ku cyorezo cya HCoV mu gihe cyashize kandi zikaba zikiza.
Iyo virusi ishobora kwandura abantu benshi cyane, ariko iyo itangiye kwandura abantu benshi cyane, ikongera ikabarinda indwara z'ibyorezo.
Kugira ngo ibyo bishoboke, HCoVs zigomba kuba zarakomotse ku bantu batunganye kugira ngo haboneke izindi nshya zishobora kurwanya inzitizi z'aho ziherereye.
Ku bw'ibyo, uko SARS-CoV-2 ibaho igihe kirekire kandi abantu benshi bakandura, ni na ko ishobora kwiyongera.
Iyo abantu bamenyereye iyo ndwara, ntibakunze kuyandura binyuze mu kwihisha cyangwa mu bundi buryo bwo kuyandura.
Mu myaka myinshi, hari ubwoko bune bwa CoVs zandura abantu zagiye zikwirakwira mu bantu, zituma abantu barwara ibicurane kandi ntibashobore kwirinda indwara.
Izo virusi ntizikeneye kwihisha mu matungo.
Mu buryo bunyuranye n'ubwo, SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV zandura cyane ntizihuza n'abantu kandi ntizifite ubushobozi bwo guhashya ikwirakwira ry'iyo virusi mu bantu.
Ibyo byatuma ikomeza kuba mu nyamaswa kandi ikagera ku bantu, akenshi ikabikora binyuze ku kintu kimwe cyangwa byinshi bishobora kuyikwirakwiza.
SARS-CoV-2 ifite ibimenyetso bisa cyane n'ibya SARS-CoV/MERS-CoV n'izindi HCoV enye zandura abantu.
Iyo virusi ifite ubushobozi bwo kwandura vuba nk'ubw'izindi HCoVs zandura abantu, nubwo ubu ari bwo bwa mbere.
Icyakora, hari izindi HCoVs zandura cyane kurusha izindi zandura abantu ariko zikaba zidakomeye cyane nka SARS-CoV cyangwa MERS-CoV.
Tuzakomeza turebe niba izaba ifite ubushobozi bwo kwihanganira abantu no kugenda mu bantu nta bikoresho cyangwa inyamaswa ziyirimo.
Mbere yo gusuzuma inkomoko ya HCoVs, byaba byiza tubanje gusuzuma ibisobanuro by'imiterere n'imiterere yayo, imiterere yayo, aho iba, aho ituruka n'ibituma ihinduka HCoVs.
Iyo HCoV ikomeje kwiyongera mu mubiri, ikura mu mikorobe, mu binyabuzima, mu binyabuzima no mu bindi binyabuzima.
Impamvu ni uko virusi ifite ubushobozi bwo kwihanganira indwara kandi ikaba idashobora kwanduza undi muntu.
Mu buryo nk'ubwo, ubwandu bwa HCoV buterwa n'ubwandu bw'ibice byinshi by'umubiri.
Muri izo ngero zombi, utwo duce duto duto duto tw'ibinyabuzima twashyizwe mu bubiko bw'indwara n'aho hantu heza ho kubikamo HCoV cyangwa virusi itera iyo ndwara.
Icyakora, iyo HCoV nshya yageze ahantu heza cyane habasha kuyirinda mbere cyangwa nyuma yo kwinjira mu bantu, ntiyihuza neza n'aho hantu hashya kandi akenshi ihitana abantu.
Iyi ndwara ishobora guterwa n'inyamaswa kandi ikagira uruhare rukomeye mu gutuma virusi ikomeza kwiyongera, ikinjira mu bantu kandi igatuma abantu benshi barwara.
HCoV ishobora kwanduza indwara ikomeye cyane iyo itarekuwe ngo ikwirakwizwe mu kindi gice cy'umubiri cyayirinda.
