Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryashyize icyorezo cya COVID-19 ku rutonde rw'indwara z'ibyorezo
Ku wa Gatatu, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryatangaje ko icyorezo cya COVID-19  cyatewe na coronavirus SARS-CoV-2  ari icyorezo.
Nubwo izina pandemiya ryerekeza ku burwayi bw'icyorezo aho kwerekeza ku buremere bwacyo, OMS yabonye ko ari ngombwa ko ubutegetsi bufata ingamba:
Ibihugu byose bishobora guhagarika iki cyorezo.
Iyo ibihugu byamaze kubona, gupima, gufasha, gushyira mu kato no guhagarika abantu, kandi bigashyira hamwe mu kurwanya iki cyorezo, niko Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus, umuyobozi mukuru wa OMS, yavuze.
Turahangayikishijwe n'uburyo byandura kandi nta kintu na kimwe kirimo gukorwa.
Dr Tom Frieden, umuyobozi wa mbere w'ikigo gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara muri Amerika, yavuze ko icyorezo ari "igitangaza".
Avuga ko, nk'uko CNN yabitangaje mu kwezi kwa kabiri, kuva icyorezo cy'ibicurane cyatangira, nta kindi cyorezo cy'ibicurane by'ubuhumekero cyigeze kibaho cyangwa ngo gikwirakwizwe ku isi.
Ghebreyesus yagize icyo avuga, avuga ko "mu bihugu byasigaye, nta cyorezo cy'icyorezo cya coronavirus kiriho".
Yakomeje agira ati, Kandi ni nde utabonye icyorezo gishobora guhagarara.
Iryo zina ry'icyorezo ryaturutse ku cyemezo cy'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) cyo ku wa mbere cyemeza ko ari ikibazo cy'ingutu ku buzima ku isi.
Dr Anthony Fauci wo mu kigo cyo muri Amerika gishinzwe indwara ziterwa n'isukari n'imyanda, yavuze ko "nyuma yaho ibintu bishobora kuba bibi kurushaho".
Ku wa Kane, raporo y'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ivuga ko mu bantu 126,000 banduye COVID-19 ku isi, 4,600 barapfuye.
Icyorezo cya coronavirus cyo mu 2019-20 ni icyorezo cya coronavirus yo mu 2019 (COVID-19), cyatewe n'indwara y'ubuhumekero ya coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Icyorezo cyamenyekanye i Whuhan mu Bushinwa mu Kuboza 2019, gitangazwa nk'icyorezo ku wa 30 Mutarama 2020, gitangazwa nk'icyorezo ku wa 11 Werurwe 2020.
Ku itariki ya 10 Mata 2020, abantu miliyoni 1.61 bari bafite COVID-19 mu bihugu 210 n'uturere, bihitana abantu 97.000.
Abantu bagera ku 364.000 barahunze.
Umubare w'abapfa ni 4% mu Bushinwa, 13.04% muri Algeria na .08% muri Nouvelle Zélande.
Ibimenyetso ni umuriro, inkorora no guhumeka nabi.
Ingorane ni indwara y'ibihaha, guhumeka nabi.
Iyo indwara yanduye uyu munsi, ibimenyetso by'indwara bishobora gutangira kugaragara mu minsi iri hagati ya itanu na cumi n'ibiri.
Nta rukingo cyangwa umuti bizwi.
Kugira ngo bakumare indwara, ugomba kubanza gukaraba intoki, kwipfuka mu mazuru cyangwa mu kanwa igihe ukoroye, kwirinda abantu, kandi ukamenya abantu bari mu kato kubera ko bari hafi y'umuntu wanduye.
Ubutegetsi ku isi hose bwashyizeho amategeko agenga imihanda, gufunga ingendo, amasaha yo kwinjira no gusohoka, ibikoresho byo kwirinda no gufunga ahantu.
Icyorezo cyateje ibibazo by'ubukungu bw'isi, gihagarika cyangwa gihagarika siporo, amadini, politiki n'imyidagaduro, ndetse n'ubukene bw'ibicuruzwa ku isi bitewe n'ibiciro by'ibicuruzwa by'umurengera.
Amashuri makuru na za kaminuza byafunzwe ku isi hose cyangwa mu mijyi mu bihugu 193, bibangamira abanyeshuri bangana na 99,4 ku ijana by'abatuye isi.
Kutamenya ukuri kuri virusi byogeye kuri interineti, kandi urwango rw'abanyamahanga rwagaragajwe cyane mu bantu bo mu Bushinwa, mu Burasirazuba no mu Majyepfo ashyira Uburasirazuba bwa Aziya no mu bihugu bihana imbibi na yo, ndetse no mu bihugu byugarijwe n'iyi virusi.
Iyo imihanda ifunze, umwuka wa karubone uba ugabanutse.
Abategetsi bo mu mujyi wa Wuhan mu Bushinwa (umurwa mukuru wa Hubei) basanze hari abantu benshi barwaye indwara y'ibicurane ku itariki ya 31 Ukuboza 2019, kandi ubushakashatsi bwo kubimenya bwatangiye mu ntangiriro za Mutarama 2020.
Abanduye bavuye mu isoko ry'amatungo rya Huanan, kandi bivugwa ko virusi yaturutse muri ako gace kandi ko ari zoonotic.
Iyi virusi yateye iyi ndwara yitwa SARS-CoV-2, virusi nshya iterwa na coronavirus y'imbeba, coronavirus y'inyoni na SARS-CoV. Umuntu wa mbere wagaragayeho ibimenyetso by'indwara yanduye ku ya 1 Ukuboza 2019, kandi ntibari bazi niba yaraturutse muri ako gace.
