Mu gihe habagaho guhagarika imodoka mu mujyi wa Wuhan na Hubei, ibihugu byinshi byateganyaga guhagarika abayobozi ba politiki mu gihe cy'indege z'igihugu, byemejwe n'abayobozi b'Ubushinwa.
Canada, Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika, Ubuyapani, Ubuhinde, Sri Lanka, Ositaraliya, Ubufaransa, Argentine, Ubudage na Tayilande ni byo bihugu bya mbere byahise byimura abaturage babyo.
Pakisitani yatangaje ko igiye gukuraho umuntu wayo mu Bushinwa.
Ku itariki ya 7 Gashyantare, Burezili yakuye muri icyo gihugu abaturage 34 b'Abanyabrezili cyangwa ababyeyi babo, ifashijwe n'abaturage bane bo muri Polonye, Umushina umwe n'Umuhinde.
Abanyapolonye, Abashinwa n'Abahindi batunganyijwe muri Polonye, Abanyabrezili batwawe n'indege bajya muri Brezili.
Abaturage ba Burezili bari bagiye i Wuhan bashyizwe mu kato mu gace kegereye ikigo cya Burezili gishinzwe kurwanya icyorezo cya Lymphoma.
Kuri uwo munsi, abantu 215 bo muri Kanada (176 bari mu ndege, 39 bari mu yindi ndege ya leta ya Amerika) bavuye mu mujyi wa Wuhan bajya mu kato ka icyumweru cya kabiri muri CFB Trenton.
Ku ya 11 Gashyantare, indi ndege yari itwaye Abanyakanada 185 yavuye i Wuhan ihagarara kuri CB Trenton.
Abategetsi ba Australasia batanze toni 277 z'ibikoresho byabo ku ya 3 na 4 Gashyantare, mu gihe abantu bo ku kirwa cya Christmas bari bamaze iminsi 14 mu kato.
Indege y'i Nouvelle Zélande yohereje abantu ku itariki ya 5 Gashyantare, abari bayirimo (bamwe muri bo bari baturutse muri Ositaraliya no mu karere ka Pasifika) bajya mu kato i Whangaparoa, mu majyaruguru ya Auckland.
Ku ya 15 Gashyantare, Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zatangaje ko zigiye gucyura Abanyamerika bari mu bwato bwa Diamond Pricess.
Ku itariki ya 21 Gashyantare, indege y'Abanyakanada 129 yari iturutse mu bwato bwa Diamond Princess yageze i Trenton, Ontario.
Mu ntangiriro za Werurwe, leta y'u Butaliyani yatangiye gucyura abaturage ba Iran. Ku ya 14 Werurwe, indege ya Leta ya Afurika y'Epfo yavanyemo abaturage 112 ba Afurika y'Epfo.
Ibizamini byakozwe, maze abantu bane bo muri Afurika y'Epfo bagaragaje ibimenyetso bya coronavirus barasigara kugira ngo barinde abandi.
Abaturage bo muri Afurika y'Epfo gusa basuzumwe bagasanga nta bwandu bafite ni bo bavuye muri icyo gihugu.
Ibizamini byakozwe ku baturage bo muri Afurika y'Epfo ndetse n'abakozi bo mu ndege, abakozi ba hoteli, abapolisi, n'abakozi bo mu biro by'indege, bose bari mu kato k'iminsi 14 muri Ranch Resort.
Ku ya 20 Werurwe, Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika zatangiye gukura ingabo zayo muri Iraki kubera icyorezo.
Ku ya 5 Gashyantare, Minisiteri y'Ububanyi n'Amahanga y'Ubushinwa yatangaje ko ibihugu 21 (harimo Delarus, Pakistan, Trinidad na Tobago, Misiri, Irani na Turukiya) byohereje imfashanyo mu Bushinwa.
Abanyeshuri b'Abashinwa bo muri Kaminuza y'Amerika bifatanyije mu bikorwa byo kohereza imfashanyo mu bice by'u Bushinwa byibasiwe cyane na virusi, kandi mu kigo kimwe cyo muri Chicago, amakariso 50,000 ya N95 yoherejwe mu bitaro byo mu ntara ya Hubei ku ya 30 Mutarama. Umuryango w'ubutabazi Direct Relie, ku bufatanye na FedEX, wohereje amakariso 200.000 n'ibindi bikoresho by'ubwirinzi, birimo bagan, barob, mu ndege y'ibikoresho by'ubutabazi ku bitaro bya Wuhan Union ku ya 30 Mutarama.
Ku ya 5 Gashyantare, Bill na Melinda Gates batangaje ko bashyize inkunga ya miliyoni 100 z'amadolari muri OMS mu bushakashatsi bw'urukingo no mu bikorwa byo gufasha no kurinda abaturage bari mu kaga muri Afurika no muri Aziya y'Amajyepfo.
Interaksyon yatangaje ko leta y'Ubushinwa yohereje udupfukamunwa 200,000 muri Filipine ku ya 6 Gashyantare, nyuma y'aho Senateri Richard Gordon yohereje udupfukamunwa miliyoni 3.16 i Wuhan.
Ku ya 19 Gashyantare, Croix Rouge ya Singapuru yatangaje ko yashyizeho inkunga ya miliyoni 2.26 z'amadolari yo gufasha Ubushinwa.
Ubuyapani bwatanze udupfukamunwa miliyoni muri Wuhan, Turukiya yatanze ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi, Uburusiya bwatanze toni 13 z'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi muri Wuhan, Maleziya yatangaje ko izatanga toni 18 z'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi mu Bushinwa, Ubudage bwatanze toni 10,000 z'imyenda y'ubuvuzi, Amerika yatanze toni 17.8 z'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi mu Bushinwa kandi ivuga ko miliyoni 100 z'amadolari zigiye gutangwa mu bihugu byugarijwe n'icyorezo. Nyuma y'aho icyorezo cya Wuhan kibonetse, igihugu cyari gisigaye kohereza imfashanyo mu bihugu byinshi byugarijwe n'icyorezo.
Muri Werurwe, Ubushinwa, Cuba n'u Burusiya byohereje ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi n'abaganga mu Butaliyani kugira ngo bifashe abaturage kurwanya coronavirus.
Umucuruzi Jack MA yohereje ibikoresho byo gupima indwara miriyoni 1,1, udupfukamunwa miriyoni 6, n'imyenda 60,000 yo kwirinda indwara i Addis Abeba muri Etiyopiya kugira ngo igabanywe n'Umuryango wa Afurika Yunze Ubumwe.
Nyuma yaho yohereje muri Panama ibikoresho byo gupima 5.000, udupfukamunwa 100.000 n'imashini 5 zo guhumeka.
Bwana Ma kandi yatanze ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi muri Kanada. U Buholandi, Esipanye, Turukiya, Jeworujiya na Repubulika ya Tchèque byatangaje ko bitewe impungenge n'udupfukamunwa n'ibikoresho byo gupima indwara biturutse mu Bushinwa.
Urugero, Espagne yanze ibipimo 58,000 bya koronavirusi byaturutse mu Bushinwa byerekanaga ko ibipimo byabyo ari 30% gusa, nyuma yaho Ubuholandi bufata ibipimo 600.000 by'ibipimo bya Mask z'Abashinwa kubera ko zari zanduye.
U Bubiligi bwasubije udupfukamunwa 100.000 tutakoreshejwe, kuko bwumvaga ko twavuye mu Bushinwa, ariko mu by'ukuri tukaba twaraturutse muri Kolombiya.
Ariko kandi, hari ibihugu byo muri Amerika y'Epfo na Afurika byitabiriye inkunga y'u Bushinwa. Ku itariki ya 2 Mata, Banki y'Isi yatangije gahunda yihutirwa yo gufasha ibihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere.
OMS yashimye imbaraga z'abategetsi b'u Bushinwa mu kurwanya no gukumira icyorezo.
OMS yavuze ko hari itandukaniro hagati y'icyorezo cya SARS cyo mu 2002-2004, aho abayobozi b'u Bushinwa bashinjwaga ko batavuze ku buryo bwumvikana neza ku bikorwa byakozwe mu kurwanya no gukumira iki cyorezo, n'icyorezo cy'ubu, aho abayobozi bazajya batanga amakuru buri gihe kugira ngo badakomeza gutera ubwoba abaturage mbere y'umunsi mukuru w'umwaka mushya.
Ku ya 23 Mutarama, nyuma y'icyemezo cy'abayobozi cyo guhagarika ubwinjira n'ubwisubirayo bwose mu mujyi wa Wuhan, Gauden Galea, uhagarariye OMS yavuze ko nubwo nta nama ihamye yatanzwe na OMS, yari igikorwa cyiza cyerekana ko hari imbaraga nyinshi zashyizweho mu gihe cy'ibihe bidasanzwe kandi ko ari ikintu kitigeze kibaho mu rwego rw'ubuzima. Ku ya 30 Mutarama, nyuma yo kumenyekana ko hari ubwandu bwanduye hanze y'Ubushinwa kandi umubare w'abarwayi ukomeje kwiyongera mu bindi bihugu, OMS yatangaje ko iki cyorezo ari icyorezo cya 6 cya Leta kibangamiye ubuzima rusange ku rwego mpuzamahanga (USPPI), PHEIC kuva hatangira ibikorwa byo guhashya icyorezo cya 2009.
Umuyobozi Mukuru wa OMS, Tedros Adhanom, yavuze ko PHEIC ishobora gukwirakwira ku isi hose, cyane cyane mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere bidafite serivisi nziza.
Nyuma yo gushyiraho amategeko yo guhagarika ingendo, Tedros yavuze ko "nta mpamvu yo gushyiraho amategeko abuza ingendo n'ubucuruzi hagati y'ibihugu" kandi ko "WHO itazongera guhagarika ingendo cyangwa ngo yemere ingendo".
Ku ya 5 Gashyantare, OMS yasabye ibihugu inkunga ya miliyoni 675 z'amadolari y'Amerika yo gushyigikira ibikorwa byo kwitegura ibihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere, ivuga ko ari ngombwa ko haboneka ubufasha bwihutirwa mu bihugu bidafite uburyo bwo kumenya abantu banduye, mu gihe habayeho icyorezo cy'icyorezo cy'icyorezo.
Tedros yakomeje avuga ko "Gushyiraho ingufu zingana n'iz'umuyoboro wacu woroshye cyane" kandi asaba ibihugu kwitanga ubu cyangwa kwishyura amafaranga menshi nyuma. Ku ya 11 Gashyantare, mu kiganiro n'abanyamakuru, OMS yatangaje ko COVID-19 ari izina ry'icyorezo.
Kuri uwo munsi, Tedros yavuze ko Umunyamabanga Mukuru wa Loni António Guterres yemeye gutanga imbaraga z'Umuryango w'Abibumbye mu kurwanya icyo cyorezo.
Itsinda ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku bibazo by'ibanze ryatangiye akazi, rituma Umuryango w'Abibumbye wose ugira uruhare muri iyo ntambara, OMS ivuga ko izagira uruhare mu kwita ku ubuzima mu gihe izindi nzego z'ubuzima zizazana ubumenyi bwazo mu by'imibereho, ubukungu n'iterambere.
Ku ya 14 Gashyantare, itsinda rya OMS mu Bushinwa ryatangiye gukora mu buryo bwagutse mu gufasha abaganga mpuzamahanga n'abakozi ba OMS mu kurwanya icyorezo no kugenzura kubangamira icyorezo n'imikorere yacyo mu baturage binyuze mu mahugurwa n'inama mu nzego mpuzamahanga zihariye no gusura ingaruka z'ibikorwa byo kurwanya icyorezo mu karere no mu gihugu, harimo n'imijyi n'imidugudu. Ku ya 25 Gashyantare, OMS yavuze ko isi ikeneye gukora byinshi mu kwitegura icyorezo cya coronavirus, ivuga ko nubwo tudashobora kuvuga ko ari icyorezo, tugomba gukora ibishoboka byose kugira ngo twitegure.
Mu rwego rwo kurwanya iki cyorezo muri Irani, OMS yoherejeyo itsinda ryo kugenzura iki kibazo. Ku ya 28 Gashyantare, abayobozi ba OMS bavuze ko ibyago byo kwandura coronavirus ku isi ari "bihanitse" ariko ko bigomba "gukomeza kwiyongera", mu rwego rwo hejuru rw'umutekano n'umutekano.
Mike Ryan, umuyobozi w'ishami ry'umuryango w'abibumbye ryita ku buzima, yatanze umuburo mu itangazamakuru ko Iki ari ikintu cy'ukuri isi yose igomba kumenya: Mukanguke.
Yavuze ko bishoboka ko virusi iri hafi kandi ko ari ngombwa kwitegura, avuga ko hakenewe ingamba zifatika zo kwirinda "ibibi byinshi" ku isi.
Ryan yakomeje avuga ko amakuru y'ubu atazagira icyo atwara inzego z'ubuzima kugira ngo zivuge ko ari ibicurane; avuga ko ibyo bivuze ko "tuzatekereza ko abantu bose ku isi bashobora kwandura iyi virusi".
Ku ya 11 Werurwe, OMS yatangaje ko coronavirus ari icyorezo.
Umuyobozi mukuru wa OMS yavuze ko afite impungenge z'ubukana n'ubukana bw'iki cyorezo, ndetse n'uko nta cyo twakora.Abantu benshi banenga OMS kubera ko batagenzura neza ibi bibazo, urugero nko gutangaza vuba ko iki cyorezo ari ikibazo cy'uburwayi bukabije kandi ko ari icyorezo.
Ku ya 6 Mata, abantu 733.000 bashyize umukono ku nyandiko isaba ko umuyobozi mukuru wa OM Tedros Adhanom yegura.
Ku ya 26 Werurwe 2020, inzobere nyinshi mu by'uburenganzira bwa muntu z'Umuryango w'Abibumbye zashyize imbaraga mu guharanira uburenganzira bwa muntu muri iki gihe cy'icyorezo cya COVID-19.
Itsinda ry'impuguke ryavuze ko abantu bose bagomba gukizwa kandi ko ubutegetsi aribwo bufite inshingano yo kubikora.
Abo bantu bavuze ko kuba nta mafaranga bafite cyangwa nta bwishingizi bw'ubuzima bafite ari impamvu yo guhohotera itsinda runaka ry'abantu.
Abahanga bavuze ko abantu bose bafite uburenganzira bwo kugira ubuzima bwiza, hakubiyemo abamugaye, abantu bake, abageze mu za bukuru, impunzi, abatagira aho baba, abakene cyane, imfungwa n'impunzi ndetse n'abantu badafite aho baba, kandi ko leta igomba kubitaho.
Guverinoma z'ibihugu zashyizeho ingamba zo guhangana n'ibibazo by'ubukungu n'imibereho byatewe n'icyorezo cya COVID-19.
Umuryango w'Ubutwererane mu by'Ubukungu n'Iterambere (OECD) washyizeho uburyo bushya kandi bwiza bwo guhuza ibihugu mu guhangana n'iki cyorezo, harimo ibitekerezo n'inama.
Mu rwego rwo kurushaho gushimangira uburyo bwo kwita ku buzima no kuzamura ubukungu ku isi mu guhangana n'ingaruka z'ibihano byo gufunga no kugabanya ingendo, ikigo cya interineti gifite uburyo bwo gukurikirana politiki y'igihugu, kandi gifasha ibihugu kwiga mu mahanga no guhangana n'icyorezo cya coronavirus.
Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika zashinje leta y'Ubushinwa, Minisitiri w'Intebe w'u Bwongereza Michael Gove, n'umuhungu wa Perezida wa Burezili, Edouardo Bolsonaro, uburyo bakiriye iki cyorezo cyatangiriye mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Bamwe mu bayobozi bakuru b'ishyaka rya gikomunisiti ry'Ubushinwa (CCP) birukanywe mu kazi kubera ko bagenzuraga ibikorwa by'Ubushinwa byo gushyira abantu mu kato mu Bushinwa bwo hagati, bikaba bigaragaza ko abaturage batazishimira uko abayobozi bo muri ibyo bihugu bitwaye.
Bamwe mu banyamakuru bemeza ko impamvu y'ibyo ari ugukingira umunyamabanga mukuru w'ishyaka ry'abakomunisiti ry'Ubushinwa Xi Jinping, kugira ngo atazagerwaho n'ingaruka z'icyorezo cya coronavirus.
Bamwe mu bayobozi b'Ubushinwa, barimo Zhao Lijian, bahakanye ko coronavirus itangiriye i Wuhan, kandi bahakana ibirego by'Amerika n'u Butaliyani ko COVID-19 ari yo yatumye ibaho.
Leta ya Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika ya Donald Trump yavuze ko coronavirus ari virusi yo mu Bushinwa cyangwa virusi ya Wuhan kandi ivuga ko Ubushinwa bwarinze iki cyorezo cy'icyorezo cy'isi, bamwe bavuga ko ari amagambo agaragaza urwikekwe rushingiye ku moko kandi ko ashinja leta ye kuba itarashoboye guhangana n'iki cyorezo.
Daily Beast yabonye telegarafe ya leta ya Amerika igaragaza ibiganiro by'inama y'umutekano w'igihugu, ivuga ko ibiganiro byose byibandaga ku Bushinwa gusa.
Twabwiwe kugerageza gukosora amakuru yose, haba mu nama y'abanyamakuru no kuri televiziyo. Politico, ikigo cy'iperereza ku mahanga na Bloomberg bavuze ko imbaraga z'Ubushinwa zo kohereza imfashanyo mu bihugu byugarijwe na virusi ari kimwe mu bikorwa byo gushaka kugira ingaruka ku isi.
Josep Borrell, umujyanama w'umuryango w'ubumwe bw'uburayi ushinzwe ububanyi n'amahanga, yaburiye ko ari "igikorwa cyo gushaka ubutegetsi binyuze mu butasi no mu buryo bwo gutanga".
Borell yavuze kandi ko Ubushinwa buzatuma hakorwa ibishoboka byose kugira ngo bube inshuti nziza kandi yizerwa, mu buryo butandukanye na Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika.
Ubushinwa bwongeye gusaba Amerika gukuraho ibihano kuri Siriya, Venezuela na Irani, buvuga ko bwohereje imfashanyo muri ibyo bihugu bibiri bya nyuma.
Udupfukamunwa 100,000 Jack Ma yohereje muri Cuba twahagaritswe ku ya 3 Mata kubera ibihano by'Amerika.
Nanone kandi, bashinja Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika ko yafashe imfashanyo zo mu rwego rw'ubukungu zohereje mu bindi bihugu kugira ngo zizibere inyungu zayo bwite.
Kandi hari ibindi bihugu byagiye byigaragambya ku birebana n'ibijyanye n'ibipfukamunwa, urugero nk'u Budage, Otirishiya, n'u Busuwisi; ndetse na Repubulika ya Tchèque mu Butaliyani.
Byongeye kandi, Turukiya yahagaritse ibikoresho byo guhumeka byari bigomba kujyanwa muri Hisipaniya.
Mu ntangiriro za Werurwe, guverinoma y'u Butaliyani yarakajwe n'uko Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi utari wagize icyo ukora ku cyorezo cya coronavirus mu Butaliyani.
Maurizio Massari, Ambasaderi w'u Butaliyani mu Muryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi, yavuze ko u Bushinwa ari bwo bwonyine bwakoze ibintu mu buryo buhuje n'ibyo bihugu byombi.
Mu by'ukuri, si ikimenyetso cyiza ku bumwe bw'i Burayi.
Ku ya 22 Werurwe, nyuma y'ikiganiro cya telefoni na Minisitiri w'Intebe Giuseppe Conte, Perezida w'u Burusiya Vladimir Putin yohereje ingabo z'Uburusiya z'abaganga, imodoka z'imiti, n'ibindi bikoresho by'ubuvuzi mu Butaliyani.
Ikinyamakuru cyo mu Butaliyani cyitwa La Stampa cyatangaje ko "umuyobozi ukomeye mu bya politiki" utifuje ko izina rye rimenyekana, yavuze ko 80 ku ijana by'inkunga Rissue yatanze "ari nta cyo yari imaze cyangwa nta cyo yari imaze ku Butaliyani".
Uyu mugabo yashinje u Burusiya gutangiza intambara zo kwigarurira ibihugu no gutsinda muri politiki.
Perezida wa Lombardy, Attilio Fontana, na Minisitiri w'Ububanyi n'Amahanga Luigi Di Maio, bahakanye ibyo bitangazamakuru kandi bashimira.
Uburusiya na bwo bwo bwohereje ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi muri Amerika.
Umuvugizi wa Kremlin, Dimitry Peskov, yavuze ko igihe inkunga yohererejwe bagenzi be bo muri Amerika, [Putin] yari yizeye ko igihe amasosiyete yo muri Amerika yari kuba asubiye mu bikorwa bya mbere, ari bwo bari kuzakora nk'ibyo bakoze igihe byari kuba ngombwa.
Imyitozo ya gisirikare ya OTAN yari iteganyijwe mu 2020 iteganyijwe kubera mu Budage, Polonye no mu bihugu bya Baltique, imyitozo ikomeye cyane ya OTAN kuva intambara y'ubutita irangiye, yasubitswe.
Kate Hudson, Umunyamabanga Mukuru wa Kampiyona yo Kurandura Ibirwanisho bya Nikleyeri, yanenze cyane imyitozo ya Defender 2020 agira ati: "Mu gihe iki cyorezo cy'indwara kihari, ntabwo byateza akaga gusa ku basirikare ba Amerika n'ibihugu byinshi by'i Burayi bizitabira iyi myitozo, ahubwo byateza n'abaturage b'ibihugu bizitabira iyi myitozo. Icyorezo kimaze igihe gito cyane kibangamiye leta ya Irani, aho abanyamuryango 12 b'inteko ishinga amategeko na 15 b'abanyapolitiki bashya n'abasanzwe bafite ubwandu bw'iyi virusi.
Perezida wa Irani Hassan Rouhani, yanditse ibaruwa isaba ubufasha ku bayobozi mpuzamahanga ku ya 14 Werurwe 2020, avuga ko igihugu cye kitazashobora guhangana n'icyorezo kubera ko kitabona isoko mpuzamahanga kubera ibihano bya Amerika kuri Irani.Iki cyorezo kizatuma Amerika ikoresha ingamba z'ingirakamaro ku baturage bo mu bihugu bikize, harimo ubuvuzi bw'isi yose, kwita ku bana, ikiruhuko cy'umuryango gihembwa, no kwifuza cyane amafaranga n'ubuvuzi rusange.
Abashakashatsi mu bya politiki batekerezaga ko bishobora kugabanya amahirwe ya Donald Trump yo gutorwa mu matora yo mu 2020. Imishyikirano ye n'Ubuyapani na Koreya y'Epfo yangiritse cyane kubera icyorezo.
Koreya y'Epfo yanenze "imihati y'Ubuyapani yo gushyira abantu mu kato idasobanutse kandi idafite ishingiro" igihe u Buyapani bwavugaga ko abantu bose baturutse muri Koreya y'Epfo bari kujya mu kato k'ibyumweru bibiri mu bigo leta yari gushyiraho.
Mu mizo ya mbere, abaturage bo muri Koreya y'Epfo ntibishimiye uko Perezida Moon Jae-in yitwaye mu kurwanya iyo virusi.
Abanyakoreya benshi bashyize umukono ku nyandiko yo kwegura kwa Moon kubera ko bumva ko adashobora kurwanya iki cyorezo, cyangwa se kubera ko bishimira ibyo yakoze.
Hari abandi bavuze ko bahangayikishijwe n'uko ibyo bituma ubutegetsi bukomeza kugira ububasha.
Muri Hongiriya, inteko ishinga amategeko yatoye uburyo bwo guha Minisitiri w'Intebe Viktor Orbán uburenganzira bwo gukomeza kuyobora burundu, gukuraho abadepite no guhagarika amatora no guhana abantu asanga bakwirakwiza amakuru y'ibinyoma ku bijyanye na virusi na gahunda ya leta yo kurwanya iki cyorezo.
Icyorezo cya koronavirusi cyatumye abantu benshi bashinjwa kutagira ibikoresho, uhereye ku kwifuza cyane ibikoresho byo kurwanya icyorezo, ibicuruzwa, n'ibikoresho by'inganda n'ibindi.
Ikigo cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika Gishinzwe Ibyo Kurya n'Imiti cyatangaje ko hari ikibazo cy'ibura ry'imiti n'ibikoresho bitewe n'uko hari abantu benshi cyane bayisabye kandi ikaba itarimo.
Nanone kandi, mu duce twinshi abantu bagiye barushaho kugura ibintu byinshi, bituma ibicuruzwa biboneka mu maduka bigabanuka, urugero nk'ibyokurya, impapuro z'isuku, n'amacupa y'amazi n'ibikoresho.
Ikigo cy'ikoranabuhanga kirimo kiratanga imiburo ikomeye ku birebana n'uko ibikoresho bya elegitoroniki bishobora gutinda gusakara.
Dukurikije uko umuyobozi mukuru wa OMS, Tedros Adhanom, yabivuze, umubare w'imyenda ikenewe mu kwirinda indwara wariyongereye incuro 100.
Ibyo byatumye ibiciro by'ibikoresho byiyongeraho incuro 12 kandi byatangaje ko ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi byari kuzaza nyuma y'amezi ane cyangwa atandatu.
Nanone kandi, bituma abantu ku isi hose batagira imyenda yo kwirinda indwara, kandi OMS itanga umuburo w'uko ibyo bishobora guteza ibibazo by'uburwayi.
Muri Ositaraliya, icyorezo cyatumye abacuruzi b'ibikombe by'inzoga za daigou babona uburyo bwo kugurisha ibicuruzwa bya Ositaraliya mu Bushinwa.
Ibi byatumye ibiribwa by'abana biboneka mu masoko manini bigabanywa ndetse na leta ya Ositaraliya irabihagarika. Nubwo umubare munini w'abantu banduye COVID-19 mu majyaruguru y'u Butaliyani no mu mujyi wa Wuhan, byateje ikibazo cy'ibiribwa, ibyo bihugu byombi byugarijwe n'ikibazo cy'ibura ry'ibiribwa.
Imyiteguro y'Ubushinwa n'u Butaliyani yagize uruhare mu kurwanya ubucuruzi bw'ibanze bw'ibiribwa, bituma ubukene bw'ibiribwa mu Burayi no muri Amerika y'Amajyaruguru bugabanuka nk'uko byari byitezwe.
Mu majyaruguru y'u Butaliyani, imirimo y'ubuhinzi yaragabanutse cyane, ariko ibiciro bishobora kwiyongera bitewe n'ibyo umusaruro utanga.
Hari abantu bake cyane bari bafite ibyokurya bike, ndetse no mu mujyi, kandi abategetsi b'u Bushinwa bashyizeho ingurube zo kubitaho.
Amategeko nk'ayo ariho mu Butaliyani asaba abacuruzi b'ibiribwa kubika ibiribwa mu gihe cy'ibiza.
