Ibizamini byo gupima indwara z'ubuhumekero ziterwa na coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19) na virusi SARS-CoV-2 bifitanye isano birimo no gupima virusi no gupima uburyo bwo kurwanya indwara.
Kuba virusi iri mu bipimo byemejwe na RT-PCR, isuzuma RNA ya coronavirus.
Ibizamini ni ibipimo by'umwihariko kandi bigamije gusa kureba RNA ya virusi ya SARS-COV-2.
Akoreshwa mu gupima indwara nshya cyangwa indwara zisanzwe.
Kugaragaza abasirikare b'umubiri (serologie) bishobora gukoreshwa mu gusuzuma no kugenzura abantu.
Ibizamini by'abasirikare b'umubiri bigaragaza umubare w'abantu banduye, harimo n'abafite ibimenyetso byoroheje cyane ku buryo bitagaragara cyangwa badafite ibimenyetso.
Ibipimo by'ukuri by'urupfu rw'abantu n'urwego rw'ubudahangarwa mu baturage bishobora kumenyeshwa n'ibisubizo by'ibizamini.
Kubera ko ibipimo bya virusi ari bike, kugeza muri Werurwe 2020, nta gihugu na kimwe cyari gifite amakuru asobanutse neza ku bijyanye n'ubwandu bwa virusi mu baturage bacyo.
Ku itariki ya 23 Werurwe, nta gihugu na kimwe cyari cyarakoze ibizamini ku bantu 3% muri rusange, kandi hari itandukaniro rinini hagati y'ibihugu byinshi.
Nanone kandi, ibyo bishobora kugira ingaruka zikomeye ku mibare y'abapfa, ishobora kuba iri hasi cyane mu bihugu byinshi.
Gukoresha uburyo bwa rRT-PCR (ritule-transcription polymerase reverse transcription) bishobora gukorwa ku bipimo by'ubuhumekero byafashwe mu buryo butandukanye, harimo no gufata igice cy'umuhogo mu mazuru cyangwa mu muhogo.
Ibisubizo bikunze kugaragara mu masaha make cyangwa iminsi ibiri.
Igishushanyo cya RT-PCR cyakozwe ku muhogo gitanga umusaruro mwiza gusa mu gihe indwara imaze icyumweru.
Nyuma y'aho, virusi ishobora kuva mu kanwa ariko igakomeza kwigwiza mu bihaha.
Ku barwayi basuzumwe mu cyumweru cya kabiri, bashobora gukorerwa isuzuma ry'amazi mu mwuka w'imbere binyuze mu cyuma cy'umuyoboro wa za karubone cyangwa mu mazi yo mu muhogo.
Imwe mu miti ya mbere ya PCR yatangijwe n'Ikigo cy'Igihugu cy'Ubugiraneza i Berlin muri Mutarama 2020 ikoresheje uburyo bwo kwandukura nyuma yo guhindura polymerase (rRT-PCR), kandi byatumye hashyirwaho ibikoresho 250,000 by'ubushakashatsi byatanzwe n'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS).
Ubwongereza na bwo bwakoze ibikoresho byo gupima ku ya 23 Mutarama 2020. Ikigo cyo muri Koreya y'Epfo Kogenebioch cyakoze igikoresho cya PC-based SARS-CoV-2 (PowerChek Coronavirusi) ku ya 28 Mutarama 2020.
