Ku ya 21 Werurwe 2020, Cepheid yahawe uruhushya na FDA rwo gukoresha ibizamini by'iminota 45 gusa.
FDA yemeje uburyo bwo gupima bukoresha isothermic nucleic acid mu cyimbo cya PCR.
Ibirenge ntibisaba guhindura ubushyuhe, ubu buryo bushobora gutanga ibisubizo mu bantu barwaye mu minota itarenze itanu na mu bantu badafite ubwandu mu minota itarenze 13.
Ubu hari imashini zigera ku 18,000 muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika, kandi abahanga ba Abbott bateganya gukora ibizamini 50.000 ku munsi. Ikigo cyo muri Tayiwani cyatangiye gukora ikizamini gikoresha umuti wa virusi itera SIDA mu gihe cy'iminota 15 kugeza kuri 20 nk'uko bigenda ku bipimo bya virusi itera SIDA.
