Ibikoresho bya CT birimo ibipimo byoroshye bya multilateral hamwe na peripheral, asymmetrical na external joint.
Umutwe w'uruti rw'umugongo uba munini cyane, ukaba ufite imbaraga nyinshi kandi ukagira imbaraga mu gihe indwara ikwirakwira.
Ubushakashatsi bwagereranyije PCR na CT mu mujyi wa Wuhan mu ntangiriro z'iki cyorezo bwagaragaje ko CT ifite ubushobozi bwo kuvura kurusha PCR, ariko ntiyagize ingaruka nziza, kandi bimwe mu bihamya byayo byerekana ko hari ubwandu bw'ibicurane n'ubundi burwayi.
Muri Werurwe 2020, Ikigo cy'Abanyamerika Gishinzwe Imikorere ya Radiyo cyatangaje ko CT idakwiye gukoreshwa mu gupima cyangwa mu gupima COVID-19. Muri Werurwe 2020, CDC yatanze inama yo gukoresha PCR mu bihe bya mbere.
