Gukaraba intoki, nanone bita isuku y'intoki, ni ugukuraho umukungugu, amavuta, mikorobe n'ibindi bintu byanduza.
Gukaraba intoki kenshi n'isabuni mu gihe cy'ingenzi ku munsi bigabanya ikwirakwira ry'indwara mu bantu benshi, urugero nk'indwara y'ibisebe, ituruka ku myanda kandi ikwirakwira mu kanwa.
Abantu bashobora no kwandura indwara zo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero nk'ibicurane cyangwa ibicurane, urugero nko kudakaraba intoki mbere yo gukora ku maso, izuru cyangwa umunwa (urugero nk'aho amazi ava).
Amasaha atanu y'ingenzi ku munsi aho gukaraba intoki n'isabune ari ngombwa ni: mbere na nyuma yo kujya guhaha, nyuma yo gusukura amabere y'umwana cyangwa kumukuraho isuka, mbere yo kugaburira umwana, mbere yo kurya no nyuma yo guteka cyangwa gukora ku nyama, amafi cyangwa inkoko.
Iyo nta mazi n'isabune bihari, ushobora gukaraba intoki n'umukungugu. Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ritanga inama yo gukaraba intoki:
Mbere yo guteka, mu gihe uteka na nyuma yo guteka.
Mbere na nyuma yo kwita ku murwayi.
Nyuma yo gukura no kwambika umwana ishashi cyangwa gukaraba umwana ukimara kuva mu bwiherero.
Nyuma yo gukorakora amazuru, gukorora cyangwa gukorora.
Nyuma yo gukora ku matungo, ku biryo byayo cyangwa ku myanda yayo.
Kugira isuku mu gihe cyo kuvura ni kimwe mu bintu by'ingenzi biranga isuku mu gihe cyo kuvura.
Gukaraba intoki mbere yo kuvura cyangwa kuvura umurwayi bishobora gutuma indwara idakwirakwira cyangwa ntizigere ikwirakwira cyane.
Impamvu ikomeye yo gukaraba intoki mu rwego rw'ubuvuzi ni ukugabanya imyanda (indwara, virusi, cyangwa mikorobe) n'ibindi bintu bishobora kutugiraho ingaruka mbi cyangwa kutugirira nabi.
Ni ingenzi ku bantu bakoresha ibiribwa cyangwa mu buvuzi, ariko ni ingenzi no ku bantu bose.
Gukaraba intoki bigira akamaro kanini ku buzima, nko kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'ibicurane, koronavirusi n'izindi ndwara; gukumira ibica uruhu; no kugabanya indwara z'ubuhumekero;
no kugabanya impfu z'abana bavukira mu ngo.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu mwaka wa 2013, bwagaragaje ko gukaraba intoki bishobora gutuma abana bari munsi y'imyaka itanu batakuza neza.
Mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere, umubare w'abana bapfa bazize indwara z'ubuhumekero n'iseru ushobora kugabanuka ari uko gusa abantu bahinduye imyifatire, urugero nko gukaraba intoki bakoresheje isabune.
Iyo ntambwe yoroheje ishobora kugabanya umubare w'abana bapfa bazize iyo ndwara ugera kuri 50%.
Ibikorwa byo gukaraba intoki bishobora gutuma abantu barwara indwara y'ibiheri inshuro eshatu, kandi ni ingenzi nk'uko bimeze ku mazi meza mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere.
48% by'ibyago byo kurwara igifu bishobora guterwa no gukaraba intoki n'isabune. Gukaraba intoki n'isabune, uburyo bworoshye kandi buhendutse bwo kwirinda indwara nk'igifu n'indwara zo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero (ARI), ni umuco w'ingenzi ugomba gukurikizwa mu ngo, mu mashuri no mu duce twose tw'isi.
Indwara y'ibihaha ifata abana cyane yitwa ARI, ni yo ahanini ihitana abana bari munsi y'imyaka itanu, buri mwaka ikaba ihitana abana bagera kuri miriyoni 1,8.
Kurwara ibicurane n'umusonga bihitana abana bagera kuri miriyoni 3,5 buri mwaka.
UNICEF ivuga ko gushyiraho gahunda yo gukaraba intoki n'isabune mbere yo kurya no nyuma yo kuva mu bwiherero bishobora kurokora ubuzima bw'abantu benshi kurusha inkingo cyangwa imiti, bikagabanya kimwe cya kabiri cy'abapfa kubera iseru n'icyorezo cy'ubuhumekero bukabije, ndetse bikagabanya n'icyorezo cy'ubuhumekero bukabije ku kigero cya kimwe cya kane.
Gukaraba intoki akenshi bikorwa mu gihe hari gahunda z'amazi, isuku n'isuku (KWISUZUMURA).
Gukaraba intoki na byo birinda indwara ziterwa no gukorana imibonano mpuzabitsina.
Ingaruka mbi gusa zo gukaraba intoki ni uko gukaraba intoki kenshi bishobora kwangiza uruhu kandi bigatuma rukomera.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe muri Danemark mu mwaka wa 2012 bwagaragaje ko gukaraba intoki cyane bishobora gutuma umuntu agira ikibazo cyo kutabona neza, indwara y'ibihaha cyangwa eczema, indwara ikunze kugaragara mu baganga.
Gukaraba intoki cyane ni kimwe mu bimenyetso by'indwara y'ihungabana (OCD).
Hari ibihe bitanu by'ingenzi aho gukaraba intoki n'isabuni ari ingenzi mu kugabanya ubwandu bw'indwara zituruka mu myanda y'umunwa: nyuma yo kuva mu bwiherero (kujya koga, guhaha), nyuma yo gukaraba umwana (kuvanaho no kwambara isutiye), mbere yo kugaburira umwana, mbere yo kurya no mbere/nyuma yo guteka cyangwa gukora ku nyama zisanzwe, nk'inyama z'inkoko.
Mu bindi bihe aho gukaraba intoki neza ari ingenzi mu kwirinda ikwirakwira ry'indwara harimo gukaraba intoki mbere na nyuma yo kuvura igikomere; nyuma yo gukorora, gukorora, gukorora amazuru; nyuma yo gukora ku myanda y'amatungo cyangwa gukorakora inyamaswa; no nyuma yo gukora ku myanda.
Mu bihugu byinshi, abantu bake ni bo bakoresha isabune mu gukaraba intoki.
Ubushakashatsi ku gusukura intoki bwakorewe mu bihugu 54 mu 2015 bwagaragaje ko ingo 38,7% zikoresha isabune mu gukaraba intoki. Mu 2014, ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko Arabiya Sawudite ifite igipimo cyo hejuru cya 97 ku ijana; Amerika iri hagati ya 77 ku ijana; naho Ubushinwa bufite igipimo cyo hasi cya 23 ku ijana. Imirimo myinshi ubu irimo guhindura imyitwarire yo gukaraba intoki n'amazi n'isabuni mu bihe by'ingenzi. Gukaraba intoki hamwe n'abanyeshuri mu masaha y'umunsi ni igitekerezo mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere cyo gushyira mu bikorwa imyitwarire y'abana.
Gahunda y'ibanze yo kwita ku buzima bwiza yageragejwe na Minisiteri y'Uburezi ya Filipine ni urugero rw'ibikorwa byo guteza imbere ubuzima bwiza bw'abana no kubamenyereza gusoma no kwandika.
Gukuraho imyanda kabiri mu mwaka, hamwe no gukaraba intoki buri munsi n'isabune, gukaraba amenyo buri munsi n'umuti w'amenyo, ni ibintu by'ingenzi muri gahunda y'igihugu.
Abagore bo muri Indoneziya bakoresha ubwo buryo, kandi bigira ingaruka nziza.
Kugira ngo umuntu akureho mikorobe ku ruhu, agomba gukoresha isabune cyangwa umuti wica mikorobe mu mazi.
Imikorere ikomeye ya sabune n'imiti yo gusukura ni ugufungura inzira yo kuvura, no kongera ubushobozi bwayo.
