Ibikoresho by'ubuziranenge byo mu kazi bikoreshwa mu kwirinda COVID-19 bikoresha uburyo bwo kwirinda no kwita ku buzima kugira ngo bibangamire ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo cya coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19).
Uburyo bwiza bwo kwirinda indwara mu kazi buterwa n'aho ukorera n'akazi ukora, ibyago byo guhura n'ibiza, ubwandu bw'indwara mu baturage, n'ibyago by'ubwandu bw'indwara ya COVID-19 ku bakozi.
Nk'uko byemezwa n'Ikigo cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika gishinzwe umutekano n'ubuzima (OSHA), akazi gafite ibyago bike ni akazi gasabwa guhura n'abandi bantu bake n'abo bakorana, gasaba gushyira mu bikorwa ingamba z'ibanze z'umutekano, nko gukaraba intoki, gukangurira abakozi kuguma mu rugo mu gihe barwaye, mu gihe barwaye indwara z'ubuhumekero, no kugira isuku n'isuku mu kazi.
Akazi k'ibyago biri hagati ni akazi gasabwa guhura kenshi cyangwa kwegerana n'abantu uzi cyangwa bashobora kuba baranduye COVID-19, ariko bashobora kurwara bitewe no guhura n'abantu benshi cyangwa gukora ingendo mu bihugu byinshi.
Ibyo ni ko bimeze ku bakozi bahura n'abantu benshi, urugero nk'abanyeshuri, abakozi n'abandi bantu benshi.
Kugira ngo abantu bo muri iki cyiciro bakire ibyago, birasaba ko, uretse ingamba rusange zo kwirinda, hakoreshwa ibikoresho by'umwuka bifite imashini zikora neza, kwirinda kuribwa no kwambara ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi mu gihe umuntu afitanye isano n'umuntu urwaye COVID-19.
OSHA ifata abaganga n'abakora mu byumba by'abapfuye nk'abantu bafite ibyago byo guhura n'umuntu ufite COVID-19 bafite ibyago byinshi, kandi bituma abantu bakora mu byuma bya aérosols cyangwa bakora cyangwa batora ibipimo by'abantu bafite cyangwa bashobora kuba bafite COVID-19.
Kurinda abantu bakora imirimo ishobora kuba irimo umwuka mubi mu nzu, no kwambara imyenda ikwiriye yo kwirinda.
Icyorezo cya COVID-19 gishobora guteza ibibazo byinshi mu kazi.
Abakozi ntibashobora kujya ku kazi kubera uburwayi, kwita ku bandi, cyangwa gutinya ko bashobora kwandura.
Imikorere y'ubucuruzi ishobora guhinduka, bitewe n'ibyo abantu bifuza kugura, n'uburyo bwo kubona ibyo bicuruzwa (urugero, kugura mu masaha y'ikiruhuko cyangwa mu buryo bwo gutanga ibitabo ku nzu).
Amaherezo, bashobora kugabanya ingendo zo gutanga ibicuruzwa mu duce dufite ubwandu bwa COVID-19. Kwitegura mbere yo kwandura bishobora kudufasha kumenya uko twakwirinda.
Imigambi igomba kureba urugero rw'ibyago biri mu kazi n'aho bakorera, harimo n'abo bahura na bo, ibyago bishobora kubaho mu ngo n'ahandi, n'ibyago abakozi nk'abageze mu za bukuru cyangwa abarwaye indwara zidakira bashobora guhura na byo.
Nanone kandi, kizasuzuma uko twakwitegura guhangana n'ibyo bibazo, n'uko twakwitegura guhangana n'ingaruka z'iyo ndwara.
Gutegura no kurwanya indwara zandura bizakurikizwa n'amategeko y'igihugu cyangwa igihugu.
Uburyo bwiza bwo guhangana n'indwara ni ugukurikirana ibibazo by'uburwayi, urugero nko kugabanya ibyago byo kwandura mu bakozi, kurinda abantu bafite ibyago byinshi byo kurwara indwara zisanzwe, gukomeza gukora, no kwirinda ingaruka ku bucuruzi bw'abandi.
Uko uzabyitwaramo bizaterwa n'uko ubwonko bwawe buzaba bumeze.
Kumenya uko umuntu wese azitwara mu kwirinda impanuka ni uburyo bwemewe bwo kurinda abakozi n'ubuzima bw'abantu benshi uko bishoboka kose.
Mu gihe nta buryo bushoboka bwo kwirinda icyorezo cya COVID-19, uburyo bwiza bwo kucyirwanya ni ugukoresha ibikoresho by'ikoranabuhanga, nyuma yo gusuzumwa n'abategetsi, hanyuma buri wese agahabwa ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi.
Kugenzura imashini bisobanura kurinda abakozi akaga ko mu kazi, ariko ntibikureho amahame mbwirizamuco, kandi bishobora kuba ari uburyo bwiza bwo gukora.
Gusuzuma abayobozi bituma habaho ihinduka mu mikorere, ibyo bikaba bisaba ko umukoresha cyangwa umukozi ahindura uburyo akoresha akazi ke.
Ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi bwite (PPE) ntibifite imbaraga nyinshi ugereranyije n'ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi cyangwa iby'abashinzwe umutekano, ariko bishobora gufasha mu kwirinda impanuka.
Uburyo bwose bw'ibikoresho bya PPE bugomba guhitamo hakurikijwe ibyago bishobora guteza umukozi, niba bikwiriye (urugero nk'ibikoresho byo guhumeka), bikagomba kwambarwa neza kandi buri gihe, bigakomeza kubikwa, kandi bigashyirwaho ibindi, niba ari ngombwa, kandi bikurwamo neza, bikogezwa, bigakorerwaho cyangwa bikirukanwe kugira ngo birinde kwandura.
Nk'uko bitangazwa n'Ikigo cy'Igihugu gishinzwe Ubuzima n'Umutekano (OSHA), impanuka zo ku kazi zidakomeye ni izisaba guhura n'abantu benshi n'abo bakorana.
Uburyo bwiza bwo kwirinda ikwirakwira ry'indwara mu kazi gashinzwe ni ugukaraba intoki kenshi, gukangurira abakozi kuguma mu rugo mu gihe barwaye, mu gihe bafite indwara z'ubuhumekero, kwambara udupfukamunwa mu gihe bakoroye cyangwa bakoroye, kugira imyenda yo guhanagura n'aho bayikura, gushyiraho ibikoresho byo gutumanaho cyangwa ibindi bikoresho mu gihe bibaye ngombwa, no kwirinda ko abakozi bakoresha ibikoresho by'abandi, no gukomeza kugira isuku n'isuku mu kazi.
Kumenya hakiri kare abantu bashobora kurwara no kubatandukanya n'abandi ni uburyo bwiza bwo kurinda abakozi, abakiriya, abashyitsi n'abandi bantu aho bakorera.
Ikigo cyo muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (CDC) gitera inkunga abakozi bafite ibimenyetso by'indwara ikomeye y'ubuhumekero kuguma mu rugo kugeza igihe umuriro, ibimenyetso by'umuriro n'ibindi bimenyetso bizaba bimaze nibura amasaha 24 bitarahindutse, kandi bagashyiraho amategeko y'ikiruhuko cy'ikiruhuko gihagije, bemerera abakozi kuguma mu rugo kugira ngo barinde abo mu muryango wabo barwaye, kandi abakozi bakamenya ayo mategeko.
Nk'uko OSHA ibivuga, ibyago byo mu kazi biri hagati y'ibyago by'ubwandu n'ibyago by'ubwandu, urugero nk'abantu bahura cyane cyangwa bari muri metero 1,8 z'abantu banduye COVID-19 cyangwa abo bahuye bashobora kwandura SARS-CoV-2 bitewe n'ubwandu bw'indwara mu karere k'aho bakorera, cyangwa se bitewe n'ingendo ziherutse gukorwa mu bihugu byanduye COVID-19.
Kurinda abakozi bahura n'abantu benshi cyane nko mu mashuri, ahantu hakorerwamo imirimo myinshi, n'ahandi hantu hari abantu benshi. Kurinda imashini z'abo bantu bisaba gushyiraho ibikoresho bikingira umwuka, guhumeka neza, ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi birinda imyuka itwara umwuka, no gushyiraho udupfukamunwa ku madirishya ku bakiriya. Kurinda abayobozi mu byiciro by'ubucuruzi by'ibyago byinshi bisaba gushishikariza abakozi barwaye kuguma mu rugo, gukora inama kuri interineti aho kuba ahantu hamwe, amategeko yo kwirinda ingendo z'abantu benshi mu bice birimo COVID-19, gushyiraho uburyo bwo kuvugana n'abantu n'ibigo by'ubucuruzi kugira ngo bakingire abantu, no guha abakozi b'abanyamwuga ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi bikenewe kugira ngo barinde COVID-19, mu gihe hari ibindi bintu bakeneye gukora, urugero nko kwambara imyenda yo kwirinda COVID-19, kwambara no kwambara ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi, kwambara imyenda yo kwifata mu gihe cy'akazi, kwambara imyenda yo kwifata, kwambara imyenda yo kwifata, kwambara neza, kwambara neza, kwambara neza, no guha abantu ibikoresho by'ubwirinda, ndetse no kubamenyesha abandi ko bakeneye kwambara neza.
Abakozi bo muri iki cyiciro ntibakenera cyane ibikoresho byo guhumeka.
Iyo umuntu arwaye mu ndege, uburyo bwiza bwo kurinda abakozi n'abandi ni ukumurinda gutandukana n'abandi ku ntera ya metero 6, gushyiraho umuntu wo mu itsinda ry'abakozi kugira ngo amwiteho, no kumwambika agapfukamunwa cyangwa kumusaba ko yambara agatambaro mu kanwa no mu mazuru igihe akoroye cyangwa akoroye.
Abakozi bo mu ndege bagomba kwambara ikanzu iyo bita ku muntu urwaye cyangwa iyo bakoreye ku mazi yo mu mubiri cyangwa ahantu hashobora kuba hari ubwandu, kandi bakagenzura cyane cyane igihe umuntu urwaye afite umuriro, ikorosi rirambye cyangwa guhumeka nabi.
Amasahani n'ibindi bikoresho by'inyongera bikoreshwa nyuma yo gutwarwa bigomba kujugunywa aho bikwiye, kandi ahantu hari ubwandu hakwiye guhanagurwa no gukingirwa. Ku bwato bw'ubucuruzi, harimo n'abagenzi n'abandi bantu bari muri ubwo bwato, kwirinda ni ukwirinda gukora ingendo mu gihe urwaye, ukirinda uburwayi kandi ukamenyesha abaganga bari muri ubwo bwato mu gihe umuntu uri muri ubwo bwato afite umuriro cyangwa ibimenyetso by'uburwayi.
Ni byiza kugenzura uko umurwayi ameze mu kigo cy'ishuri. Ku mashuri cyangwa ibigo byita ku bana, CDC isaba ko hafungwa igihe gito kugira ngo haboneke uburyo bwo kugabanya cyangwa guhashya indwara mu gihe umurwayi yabaga ari mu kigo cy'ishuri, haba mu gace k'aho ubaye cyangwa mu gihe hari icyorezo.
Iyo abantu badafite ibyago byinshi byo kwandura, ingamba zo kwirinda guhura zirashobora gufatwa nko kugabanya ingendo, amakoraniro n'andi makoraniro akomeye nk'imyitozo ngororamubiri cyangwa kuririmba mu mashuri cyangwa gusangira mu maresitora, harimo intera hagati y'ibiro, gutegereza igihe cyo kuza cyangwa kugenda, kwirinda gusura abantu bitari ngombwa, no gukoresha amazu y'ubuvuzi yihariye ku bana bafite ibimenyetso bya grippe.
Iyo hari icyorezo mu karere k'iwanyu, uretse uburyo bwo kwirinda, amashuri ashobora gufungwa by'agateganyo. Ku bapolisi bakora akazi kabo ka buri munsi, CDC ivuga ko bafite ibyago byo kwandura biri hasi.
Abashinzwe umutekano bagomba guhura n'abantu banduye cyangwa bashobora kuba baranduye COVID-19, bagomba gukurikiza amabwiriza nk'ay'abaganga, harimo kwambara ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi.
Iyo umuntu afashwe n'umuntu mu gihe akomeretse, aba bantu bagomba kubanza gusukura no guhanagura udukingirizo ku bikoresho byabo mbere yo kubikoresha, bakoresheje imashini zihumanya kandi bakurikiza amabwiriza yo kwirinda no gutakaza ibikoresho bya PPE, hamwe n'amabwiriza yo gusukura no kumesa imyenda.
OSHA ifata abakozi bamwe na bamwe bo mu buvuzi n'abo mu bigo by'ubuvuzi nk'abari mu kaga gakomeye cyangwa mu bantu bafite ibyago bikomeye.
Imirimo y'ubuvuzi y'ibanze irimo kubyara, kwita ku barwayi, gukora mu mavuriro, no gutwara abarwayi banduye cyangwa bashobora kuba baranduye COVID-19.
Bakunze kugira ibyago byo kwandura iyo bakoresheje imiti icanye, cyangwa bakorakoranya ibipimo byafashwe n'abantu barwaye cyangwa bashobora kuba barwaye COVID-19.
Imikorere ya aerosol ni ibikorwa birimo guterwa intanga, kuvura iseru, bronchoscopy, cyangwa ibindi bikorwa cyangwa ibizamini by'amenyo, cyangwa gufata ibipimo.
Ibyago by'umwihariko byo gukora mu bigo by'ubupfumu ni abakora mu byumba by'abapfuye cyangwa abakekwaho kuba barwaye COVID-19, kandi bashobora kugira ibyago byinshi iyo bamaze gupimwa bakamenya icyateye urupfu. Ibyago by'umwihariko ni igihe bakorera abantu bafite COVID-19 cyangwa bakekwaho kuba barwaye COVID-19 mu byumba byabo, ndetse no mu gihe bakora imirimo yo mu bwoko bwa aérosol.
Gushyiraho imashini zitanga umwuka mu gihe umuntu arwaye bishobora kuba byiza mu bitaro bimwe na bimwe no mu bigo by'abicanyi.
Ibipimo bigomba gukoreshwa hakurikijwe igipimo cy'ubuziranenge cya 3.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ritanga inama yo gushyira abarwayi mu byumba bitandukanye byo gutegereza bitewe n'uko bagaragayeho ubwandu bwa COVID-19. Usibye inama yo gukoresha ibikoresho byo guhumeka birimo PPE, OSHA irasaba ko abantu bakorera ahantu kure y'ibirenge 6 n'abantu bazwi ko barwaye SARS-CoV-2, bakorana na bo, cyangwa bakandujwe, ndetse no gukora imirimo y'ibinyabutabire.
Muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, ibikoresho byo guhumeka bya N95 byemejwe na NIOSH cyangwa birenze bigomba gukoreshwa cyane mu bikorwa byo kwirinda indwara zo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero nko gupima, gutoza no gusuzuma abaganga.
Ubwoko bw'imfashanyo zo guhumeka ni bwo bw'ingenzi mu kurinda no mu gutuma abantu bakora neza. OMS ntiyemera ko abantu bambara imyenda yo mu maso yose, kuko COVID-19 ari indwara y'ubuhumekero kandi idashobora gukwirakwira mu mazi yo mu mubiri.
OMS iracyasaba ko abaganga bakoresha udupfukamunwa mu gihe bakora ibizamini.
Ku bantu bafata ibipimo by'indwara z'ubuhumekero, babitaho, cyangwa batwara abantu barwaye COVID-19 badafite ibikoresho byo mu bwoko bwa aérosol, OMS irasaba ko bakoresha udupfukamunwa, indorerwamo zo kurinda, cyangwa ibikoresho byo kurinda mu maso, amakanzu n'imyenda.
Niba ukora imirimo yo mu bwoko bwa aérosol, aho gukoresha agapfukamunwa, jya ukoresha ibikoresho byo guhumeka bya N95 cyangwa FFP2.
Kubera ko ibikoresho byose bitangwa na OMS bitemewe, OMS irasaba kugabanya ibikoresho bya PPE mu buvuzi hakoreshejwe telefoni, kwirinda guhura n'abantu benshi nko gufungura amadirishya, kwemerera abaganga kwinjira mu cyumba cy'umurwayi wa COVID-19, gukoresha gusa ibikoresho bya PPE bikenewe mu buryo bwihariye, gukomeza gukoresha ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi by'ubwoko bumwe mu gihe ugiye kuvura abarwayi benshi, kubungabunga no gukoresha neza ibindi bikoresho bya PPE, no kugabanya gukoresha udupfukamunwa ku bantu badafite ibimenyetso.
