Angiotensin converting enzyme 2 (ACE2) ni enzyme iboneka mu bice by'inyuma by'ibihaha, mu mitsi, mu mutima, mu mpyiko no mu mara.
ACE2 ihagarika ingufu za angiotensin-enzyme conversion (ACE) igabanya ingano ya angiotensin-II kandi igatuma ingano ya angiotensin-II yiyongera (((1-7) bigatuma ikoreshwa cyane mu kuvura indwara z'umutima. ACE2 kandi ifasha mu kwinjiza coronaviruses.
Hari ubwoko bw'ingirabuzimafatizo mu bantu bwitwa hACE2.
Angiotensin conversion enzyme 2 ni metaloenzyme iboneka mu gice cy'inyuma cy'umubiri n'ibindi bice by'umubiri.
Poroteyine ya ACE2 ifite N-terminal peptidase M2 na C-terminal receptor y'umuhogo utwara amino acide.
ACE2 ikora nk'indimu y'indimu imwe, ikora nk'imashini ikora mu byuma byo hanze y'ingirabuzimafatizo n'ibindi bice by'umubiri.
Urubuga rwo hanze y'ingirabuzimafatizo rwa ACE2 ruva ku mubyimba rukagera ku wundi muti witwa sheddase, hanyuma poroteyine igatangira kwinjira mu maraso hanyuma ikagenda mu maraso.
ACE2 iboneka mu ngingo nyinshi: ACE2 ifatanye n'urusobe rw'ingirabuzimafatizo z'ibihaha z'ubwoko bwa II, ingirabuzimafatizo z'amahembe mato, imitsi n'imiyoboro y'amaraso n'ingirabuzimafatizo z'umushongi.
Nanone, ACE2 mRNA iboneka mu gice cy'ubwonko cyitwa cortex, mu gice cyitwa striatum, mu gice cyitwa hypothalamus no mu gice cyitwa brainstem.
Uruhare rwa mbere rwa aCE2 ni uruhande rwa ACE.
ACE ifata ingirabuzimafatizo ya angiotensin I ikongera ingirabuzimafatizo ya angiotensin II ikongera ingirabuzimafatizo ya angiotensin II.
ACE2 ifatanwa na amino acide phenylalanine yo mu gice cy'umushongi wa karuboni na angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-pPhe) maze ikongera ikongera ikongera ikongera ikongera amazi mu gice cy'umuvuduko w'amaraso (angiotensin 1-7) (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
ACE2 ishobora no guhuza na za peptides nyinshi, urugero nka [des-Arg9]-bradykinin, apelin, neurotensin, dynorphin A, na ghrelin.
ACE2 kandi itera imbunda mu gice cy'urwungano rw'umushongi wa amino acide udafite aho uhuriye na SLC6A19 kandi warwaye indwara ya Hartnup.
Uretse poroteyine yo mu rwego rw'urusobe, ACE2 ni yo ifite ubushobozi bwo kwinjira mu ngirabuzimafatizo za koronavirusi, kimwe na HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (virusi ituruka kuri SARS); na SARS-CoV-2 (virusi ituruka kuri COVID-19).
Mu buryo bwumvikana neza, guhuza igice cy'umushinge wa poroteyine S1 ya SARS-CoV na SARS-CoV2 na enzyme ya ACE2 ku rwego rw'ingirabuzimafatizo bizatuma habaho endocytosis no kuyobora virusi ya enzyme hamwe na imwe muri endosomes ziri mu ngirabuzimafatizo.
Urubuga rwo kwinjira rusaba ko poroteyine S ihindagurika ikagira uruhare muri TMPRSS2 ya serine protease, ubu irimo gusuzumwa nk'umuti ushobora kugira ingaruka nziza. Ibi byatumye abantu bamwe na bamwe bagabanya ACE2 mu ngirabuzimafatizo, mu kugerageza kurwanya ubwandu.
Icyakora, inzego z'ubushakashatsi n'iz'amategeko zemeza ko ACE n'imiti ikoreshwa mu kurwanya ARB ari byo byonyine bikwiye gukoreshwa.
Isesengura ry'imikorere n'inyigo ya meta ryasohotse ku ya 11 Nyakanga 2012 ryagaragaje ko gufata ACE bigabanya ibyago byo kurwara pneumonie ku kigero cya 34%.
Ariko kandi, ibyago byo kurwara umusonga byagabanutse no ku bantu bavurwaga ACE bari bafite ibyago byinshi byo kurwara umusonga, nk'abafite ibibazo by'umutima.
Kuvurwa kwa ACE kandi byagize uruhare mu kugabanya indwara y'ibihaha n'urupfu, ariko ingaruka zabyo zari nke ugereranyije n'ibyago byo kurwara ibihaha.
Umuntu uvura ACE2 (rhACE2) ni uburyo bushya bwo kuvura indwara z'ibihaha, kandi bwagiye bukoreshwa mu kuvura indwara y'ubuhumekero bw'ibihaha n'ubushyuhe mu ngurube zifite ikibazo cy'ubuhumekero budafite ubushobozi bwo guhumeka.
Igihe gito cy'ubuzima bwa rhACE2 mu bantu ni amasaha 10 kandi ikora mu minota 30 mu gihe cy'amasaha 24.
Ubushakashatsi bwinshi bugaragaza ko rhACE2 ishobora kuba umuti mwiza ku barwayi barwaye indwara z'ubuhumekero ziterwa n'umuvuduko ukabije wa RAS (Renin-angiotensin inhibitors) cyangwa indwara ziterwa n'umuvuduko ukabije wa angiotensin. RhACE2 irimo gusuzumwa mu buvuzi mu kuvura indwara z'ubuhumekero.
Porogaramu za BCOVID-19 ni porogaramu za telefoni zigenewe gukurikirana abantu bashobora kuba baranduye icyorezo cya coronavirus cya 2019-20. Urugero, uburyo bwo kumenya (abantu) bashobora kuba bari kumwe n'umuntu wanduye.
Hari n'ibindi bikorwa byinshi byakozwe, kandi mu duce tumwe na tumwe leta yarabigizemo uruhare.
Uburyo bwinshi bwo kugenzura abantu bwakoreshejwe mu gukoresha porogaramu za telefoni.
Abantu ntibakunda ko abantu bareba mu buryo bw'amayobera, nk'uko bigenda ku bikoresho byo kugenzura aho abantu bari.
Mu bintu by'ibanga bitagomba kwitabwaho cyane ni ibimenyetso bya Bluetooth bizajya bimenyesha umuntu igihe ari hafi ya telefone zindi.
Ku ya 10 Mata 2020, Google na Apple byatangaje ko bizashyiraho uburyo bwo gukoresha porogaramu ya Bluetooth kuri Android na iOS.
Mu Bushinwa, leta y'Ubushinwa ifatanyije na Alipay, bashyizeho porogaramu ifasha abaturage kumenya niba bari hafi y'umuntu wanduye COVID-19.
Ni gahunda ikorerwa mu mijyi 200 yo mu Bushinwa, muri Singapore, hari porogaramu yitwa TraceTogether iri gukorwa.
Abahanga mu by'ikoranabuhanga bo muri ako gace bakoze porogaramu, bayishyira ku mugaragaro kandi bayishyira mu bikorwa na leta. Macedonia ya Ruguru yashyizeho porogaramu ya Bluetooth yitwa StopKorona!, ikora igenzura ry'imikorere y'umuntu ku muntu ufite ubwandu kandi igafasha leta mu kurwanya indwara.
Porogaramu yakozwe na Minisiteri y'Itumanaho n'Ikoranabuhanga muri Minisiteri y'Ubuzima.
Ku ya 14 Mata 2020, porogaramu yari itegereje kwemerwa na Google Play na Apple App Store.
Ku ya 12 Mata, guverinoma yatangaje ko porogaramu yo gukurikirana abantu imaze kugera ku rwego rwo hejuru, kandi ko izatangira gukoreshwa mu byumweru biri imbere. Porogaramu nk'izo zirimo gukorwa muri Irilande, n'Ubufaransa (StopCovid).
Australia na Nouvelle-Zélande bifuza gukoresha porogaramu z'ikoranabuhanga z'i Singapour zirimo TraceTogether na BlueTrace. Uburusiya burimo gukora porogaramu yo kumenya abantu banduye COVID-19 baba i Moscou, kugira ngo babashe gukurikiranwa no kugenzurwa.
Ross Anderson, umwarimu wigisha iby'umutekano mu buhanga muri Kaminuza ya Cambridge, yavuze ko hari ibintu byinshi bishobora gukorwa n'izi porogaramu, harimo n'ibinyoma, kandi ko bigoye gukora neza kubera ko porogaramu ishobora gukoreshwa gusa n'abantu bake.
Mu rwego rwo kwirinda ingaruka ziterwa n'icyorezo cya coronavirus, Apple yashyizeho imipaka ku bigo byemerewe gushyira porogaramu muri App Store, ikagabanya gusa abakozi ba leta cyangwa imiryango izwi.
Google na Amazon na byo byashyizeho amategeko nk'ayo.
Abantu benshi bahanganye n'ikibazo cy'ibanga ry'abantu ku bw'inyungu z'ubugenzuzi, bibaza niba hari aho bakorera mu buryo bwemewe n'amategeko, kandi niba bashobora guhungabana nyuma ya coronavirus.
Amnesty International n'andi mashyirahamwe agera ku 100 yasabye ko hashyirwaho amategeko agenga ibikorwa byo gukurikirana.
Amashyirahamwe yashyize ahagaragara ibintu birindwi leta ishobora gukurikiza:
Kugenzura bigomba gukorwa mu buryo bwitondewe kandi bufite ireme.
Hari igihe cyo kuruhuka;
Imibare izakorwa gusa kubera COVID-19;
Bagomba kuba ari abantu ku giti cyabo kandi ntawe ugomba kubamenyesha ko babikora;
Gukurikirana hakoreshejwe mudasobwa ntibigomba kuba bishingiye ku rwikekwe;
Gutanga umubare w'abantu hanze y'akazi ugomba kubahirizwa n'amategeko yanditse;
Hakwiye kubaho uburyo bwo kurinda abaturage no gufasha mu gihe hari umuntu ubabaye kubera uyu mukozi;
Gushyiraho buri wese muri iki gikorwa ku bantu bose birakenewe, harimo n'abakozi b'ubuzima n'abatabasha kwibeshaho. German Chaos Computer Club (CCC) na Reporters Without Borders (Reporter ohne Grenzen) (RSF) na bo banditse inama zabo.
Google na Apple bateganya ko ubwo buryo bwo kugenzura buzavanwaho igihe nta mpamvu buzaba bukiriho.
Ibihugu bimwe na bimwe byemeye gukurikirana abantu hakoreshejwe ikoranabuhanga aho gukoresha porogaramu, bityo ntibisaba ko abantu bakoresha porogaramu kandi bashobora kwirinda gukurikiranwa.
Muri Israel, gukurikirana hakoreshejwe interineti byemewe.
Nanone kandi, kureba mu buryo budahuje n'ubwenge ni ukureba ibintu bitari ngombwa.
Ariko kandi, si buri buryo bwose bukeneye kumenya aho umuntu ari; uburyo bwinshi bwo kugenzura abantu bugendera ku buryo bwo guhanahana amakuru (reba igice kiri hasi aha).
Muri Koreya y'Epfo, bahinduye uburyo bwo gukoresha ikoranabuhanga.
Mu gukoresha porogaramu, amakuru yatanzwe ku mihanda myinshi, harimo telefoni, amakarita y'imari, kandi yakoreshejwe mu kumenyesha abantu ubutumwa bugufi bw'ubwandu.
Kandi abo bantu bari baranyuze muri iyo nzira barabimenyeshejwe, kandi leta yatumye abantu bose bamenya aho hantu, ibintu byari byemewe n'amategeko kubera ko byabereye mu gihugu cy'icyorezo cya MERS.
Amakuru ashobora kuboneka ku mbuga za interineti n'imbuga za interineti. Ibihugu byinshi nk'u Budage byashakaga gukoresha uburyo bwo kugenzura abaturage.
Kugeza ku ya 6 Mata 2020, nta nyandiko yari yarasohotse.
Kugenzura biramenyekana, hakurikijwe ubushakashatsi bwinshi kuva mu 2013.Ku ya 7 Mata 2020, abanyeshuri barenga icumi na babiri bakoraga ibikoresho by'ikoranabuhanga bigenzura abantu, nk'ikoranabuhanga rya Bluetooth Low Energy (BLE) ritanga amakuru y'igihe telefoni iri hafi.
Icyakora, PEPP-PT ni porogaramu ikora neza cyane hagati y'ibikoresho byo hanze, kandi nta buyobozi bufatika buhari bwo kuyikoresha. Porogaramu zo hanze zirimo Decentralized Privacy-Preserving Proximity Tracing (DP-PPT/DP-3T), Temporary Contact (TCN. fka Contact Event Numbers, CEN) Privacy Sensible Protocols na Telephone Tracking Mechanisms.
Iyo porogaramu ntizabuza abantu kuvugana, kandi ibyo byose bizakorerwa kuri telefoni.
Itsinda rya Prive na MIT Media Lab barimo gukora SafePaths, uburyo bwo gukoresha amakuru y'ibanga mu gihe cyo kuyakura no gufasha mu gukurikirana aho abantu bahurira kugira ngo bakomeze gukurikirana ikwirakwira rya COVID-19.
Bishingiye ku bushakashatsi bwakozwe mu nyandiko y'umweru Apps Gone Rogue: Kurinda amakuru y'abantu mu gihe cy'icyorezo  Bwasohotse muri Werurwe 2020. Ikindi gikorwa cyakozwe na SafeTrade ya Enigma MPZ, ikigo cy'ikoranabuhanga mu kurinda amakuru cyatangiye gukora mu kigo cya MIT Media Lab.
SafeTrade ifasha ikoranabuhanga ry'ikoranabuhanga ry'ibanga kugira ngo abantu bahitemo niba bashaka gutanga amakuru y'aho bari n'amakuru y'ubuzima bwabo ku bandi bantu ndetse n'abategetsi, ariko ntibahungabanye amategeko agenga amakuru.
Ku ya 5 Mata 2020, Ishyirahamwe mpuzamahanga rya TCN ryatangijwe n'itsinda ry'abantu b'ibanze, kugira ngo abantu barusheho kugabanya ibikomere, kandi bagire uruhare mu gutuma isi ikorana neza binyuze mu gukurikirana no kwemeza porogaramu, byari ngombwa ko ikoreshwa ku isi hose.
Ku ya 9 Mata 2020, guverinoma ya Singapuru yatangaje ko ifite amabwiriza ya BlueTrace akoreshwa n'abayobozi bayo.
Ku ya 10 Mata 2020, Google na Apple, ibigo by'ubucuruzi by'ibikoresho bya Android na IOS, byatangaje ko hagiye gutangira umushinga wo gushyigikira gukurikirana abantu ariko no kurinda ubuzima bwite bw'abantu, hakoreshejwe ikoranabuhanga rya Bluetooth Low Energy hamwe n'ibikoresho by'ibanga bya Cryptography.
Nanone kandi, basohoye inyandiko igaragaza ikoranabuhanga ry'ibanze.
