Ihingwa ry'umuti (nanone witwa umuti) ni uburyo bwo kuvura indwara cyangwa imimerere yateguwe.
Ni ijambo rikoreshwa mu bushakashatsi bwa siyansi bugamije gushaka umuti wa COVID-19.
Ubushakashatsi bukomeje mu gushaka urukingo rwa COVID-19 no guterwa amaraso. SARS-CoV-2 ifite imiti 66, yose ifite ligand yayo.
Kumenya aho umuntu ahuriye n'indi ndwara bituma habaho ubushakashatsi ku bushobozi bw'umuti wa COVID-19.
Kubera ko SARS-CoV-2 ifite akamaro gakomeye, poroteyine ni nk'impapuro za papain za protease, RNA ya RNA polymerase, helicase, poroteyine ya S, na ADP ribophosphatase.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe na Dr. Hussein AA bwagaragaje ko abantu benshi bashoboye gusobanukirwa neza uko uruhu rw'umubiri rw'umuntu rwari rukora kugira ngo hamenyekane niba hari umuti ushobora gutuma habaho ubushakashatsi ku muti wa SARS-CoV-2 nk'uko bigenda iyo habonetse umuti.
Chloroquine ni umuti wa cyera ukoreshwa mu kuvura indwara z'ubushobozi bw'umubiri bwo kwirinda indwara.
Ku ya 18 Werurwe, OMS yatangaje ko Chloroquine na Hydroxychloroquine ari byo bizashyirwa mu byiciro bine by'imiti y'umushinga w'igerageza ry'imiti.
Guverineri wa New York, Andrew Cumo, yatangaje ko igerageza ry'umuti wa chloroquine na hydroxychloroquine mu mujyi wa New York rizatangira ku ya 24 Werurwe. Ku ya 28 Werurwe, FDA yemeje hydroxychloroquine sulfate na chloroquine phosphate mu buryo bwemewe n'amategeko (USA) bwo kwivuza.
FDA ntabwo yemeje ibizamini by'umuti ariko byemejwe muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika nk'umuti wo gupima ku barwayi bafite ibyago byinshi byo kwandura ariko bakaba bari mu bitaro ariko badashobora kuvurwa.
CDC ivuga ko imikoreshereze, dosiye, n'igihe kirekire bya hydroxychloroquine mu kuvura SARS-CoV-2 bitamenyekanye.
Abaganga bavuga ko iyo miti ikoreshwa iyo nta yandi mahitamo ariho.
Ubushakashatsi bwo muri Turukiya bukorerwa i Istanbul bugamije kureba uko chloroquine ikora iyo ivanze na Zinc, Vitamini A, Vitamini C na Vitamini D.
Ubushakashatsi bukomeye burakorwa muri Kaminuza ya Duke na Kaminuza ya Oxford.
Ishuri ry'ubuvuzi rya NYU Langone ririmo kugerageza kureba akamaro n'imikorere ya hydroxychloroquine.
Mu Bushinwa, igerageza ry'urukingo rwa Wuhan na Shenzhen ryerekanye ko Favipavir ifite ubushobozi bwo kuvura indwara zidakira.
Abarwayi 35 bo mu mujyi wa Shenzhen bagaragaweho indwara mu minsi 4, ariko ubwiyongere bw'ubwandu bwari iminsi 11 mu barwayi 45 bataravurwa.
Mu bushakashatsi bwakorewe i Wuhan ku barwayi 240 barwaye indwara y'ibihaha, kimwe cya kabiri cyabo bahawe favipiravir ikindi bahawe umifenovir.
Ikigo cy'Ubutabire mu Butaliyani cyatanze inama ku bipimo by'umushinga w'ubuvuzi mu ntangiriro.
Ku ya 2 Mata, Ubudage bwatangaje ko buzakura uru rukingo mu Buyapani, bukoresheje imashini zitwara imiti mu bitaro bya kaminuza, aho ruzakorerwa ubuvumbuzi mu kuvura abarwayi ba COVID-19.
Nk'uko byatangajwe n'ikinyamakuru South China Morning Post, Shinzo Abe yaburiye ibiro bya Trump ku bijyanye no kugura uwo muti. Uyu muti ushobora kuba udafite imbaraga nyinshi ku bantu barwaye cyane kandi virusi ikomeje kwiyongera mu mubiri.
Bishobora kuba bidakwiriye ku bagore batwite cyangwa bashaka gutwita.
Icyiciro kimwe cya lopinavir/ritonavir (Kaletra), ihuriro rya lopinavir na ritonavir, cyatanze umusaruro Utarimo cyane.
Iyi miti ikoreshwa mu kurwanya ikwirakwira rya virusi itera SIDA mu mubiri.
Itsinda ry'abashakashatsi bo muri Kaminuza ya Colorado barimo gukora ubushakashatsi kuri iyi miti kugira ngo bakore umuti urwanya SARS-CoV-2.
OMS yashyize lopinavir/ritonavir mu igerageza ry'umuti ku isi.
Remdesivir yakozwe na Gilead Sciences mu rwego rwo kuvura Ebola na Marburg. Gilead Sciences yemeje ko Remdesivir ifite ubushobozi bwo kurwanya virusi nyinshi zo mu bwoko bwa phylum, pneumonia, paramyso, na corona.
