Ibipimo byagiye bihinduka mu bice bitandukanye kandi binyuze mu gihe kandi bigaterwa n'umubare munini w'abanduye, uburambe bw'ubuvuzi, amahitamo y'ubuvuzi, igihe cy'icyorezo cya mbere, hamwe n'ibintu biranga abaturage nk'imyaka, igitsina, n'ubuzima rusange.
Mu mpera z'umwaka wa 2019, OMS yatanze amabwiriza y'ibanze y'ibikoresho bya ICD-10 by'ibikoresho bya U07.1 ku bantu bapfuye bishingiye ku bipimo byemejwe n'ibigo by'ubushakashatsi ku ndwara ya SARS-CoV-2 na U07.2 ku bantu bapfuye bishingiye ku bipimo by'ubuvuzi cyangwa ku bipimo bya epidemiyoloji bya COVID-19 bitemejwe na ibigo by'ubushakashatsi ku ndwara ya SARS-CoV-2.
Dukurikije imibare ya Kaminuza ya Johns Hopkins, igipimo cy'isi yose cy'abamaze kwicwa n'icyorezo cya malariya ni 6.9% (153,822/2,240,191) kuva ku ya 17 Mata 2020.
Imibare igenda itandukana. Ibipimo bimwe na bimwe birimo igipimo cy'urupfu (CFR), kigaragaza umubare w'abantu bagaragaweho indwara bapfa bazize iyo ndwara, n'igipimo cy'urupfu rw'indwara (IFR), kigaragaza umubare w'abantu bagaragaweho indwara (yaba izisanzwe cyangwa izitarasanzwe) bapfa bazize iyo ndwara.
Iyi mibare ntabwo ihuje n'igihe, ahubwo ikurikirana umubare w'abaturage runaka uhereye ku burambe bw'ubwandu kugeza ku ndwara.
Nubwo abantu bose batagira ibyago byo kwandura, kuba bafite ibinyabuzima bishobora gutanga amakuru ku mubare w'abantu bashobora kwandura.
Mu gace k'ibanze k'icyorezo mu Butaliyani, Castiglione d'Adda, umudugudu muto utuwe n'abantu 4.600, 80 (1.7%) ni bo bamaze gupfa.
Mu gace ka Gangelt, icyorezo cyaturutse mu birori bya Carnaval, cyibasira abana bakiri bato, gihitana umubare muto w'abantu kandi si ko abantu bose bishwe na COVID-19 bashyizwe muri urwo rutonde.
Byongeye kandi, gahunda y'ubuvuzi y'Abadage yari ifite ibibazo byinshi.
Mu Buholandi, 3% by'abantu bashobora kuba bafite abasirikare b'umubiri, nk'uko bigaragazwa n'abatanga amaraso.
Abantu 69 (0,004% by'abatuye isi) nibo bamaze kumenyekana ko bishwe na COVID-19.
Ibipimo by'indwara z'ibyorezo n'ubwandu bitandukanye ku bagabo no ku bagore.
Umubare w'abicanyi mu bagabo urenze uw'abashakashatsi bose bo mu Bushinwa no mu Butaliyani.
Ibyago byo kwandura byongereye ku bagabo bageze mu myaka 50, maze icyuho cy'abagabo mu kazi k'ubucuruzi kigabanuka kigera ku myaka 90.
Mu Bushinwa, umubare w'abapfa wari 2.8 ku ijana ku bagabo na 1.7 ku ijana ku bagore.
Impamvu ituma habaho itandukaniro hagati y'abagabo n'abagore ntizwi neza, ariko ishobora kuba ishingiye ku miterere y'ibinyabuzima cyangwa ku mico.
Itandukaniro ry'ubushobozi bw'umubiri bwo kwirinda indwara bitewe n'igitsina, kunywa itabi ku kigero gito mu bagabo ndetse no kwiyongera kw'ibibazo by'ubwandu bw'ibitsina nk'umuvuduko w'amaraso uri hejuru mu myaka y'amavuko kurusha mu bagabo bishobora kongera umubare w'abapfa mu bagabo.
Mu Burayi, 57% by'abanduye ni abagabo naho 72% by'abahitanywe na COVID-19 ni abagabo.
Muri Mata 2020, leta y'Ubulayi ntiyari ifite imibare y'abantu banduye COVID-19.
Ubushakashatsi bugaragaza ko indwara ziterwa na virusi nka Ebola, HIV, ibicurane na SARS zigira ingaruka zitandukanye ku bagabo n'abagore.
Umubare wiyongereye w'abakozi b'ubuzima, cyane cyane abaforomo, ni benshi, bityo bafite ibyago byinshi byo kwandura virusi.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryemeje ku ya 11 Gashyantare 2020 ko izina ry'ubutegetsi ry'iki cyorezo rizaba "COVID-19".
Umuyobozi wa OMS, Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus, yasobanuye ko CO ari coronavirus, VI ni virus, D ni disease, kandi ko icyorezo cyamenyekanye bwa mbere tariki ya 31 Ukuboza 2019.
Ibirango byatoranyijwe mu rwego rwo kwirinda kwerekana urutoki mu gace runaka (urugero, Ubushinwa), cyane cyane ubwoko bw'inyamaswa cyangwa itsinda ry'abantu, mu buryo bwemewe n'amategeko mpuzamahanga ku izina ry'ikirango, biterwa n'uko byatuma abantu badahabwa agaciro. Virusi itera COVID-19 yitwa SARS-CoV-2 (coronavirus y'indwara y'ubuhumekero idakira).
OMS ikomeza ivuga ko ikoresha "virusi ya COVID-19" na "virusi itera COVID-19" mu itangazamakuru.
Byombi indwara na virusi byitwa gusa "coronavirus".
Mu gihe icyorezo cya mbere cyatangiraga mu mujyi wa Wuhan mu Bushinwa, virusi n'indwara byombi byitwaga "coronavirus" na "Wuhan coronavirus".
Muri Mutarama 2020, OMS yasabye ko 2019-nCov na 2019-nCoV indwara y'ubuhumekero idakira nk'amazina y'ibanze ya virusi n'indwara nyuma y'inyemezabuguzi yo mu 2015 aho gufata amazina y'indwara n'indwara.
Amazina y'ibanze COVID-19 na SARS-CoV-2 yasohotse ku ya 11 Gashyantare 2020.
Mu rwego rwo kurenga ibipimo by'urusobe rw'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi, bamwe mu bakora ibikoresho bya elegitoroniki barimo gucapa ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi nk'udupira tw'umuhogo n'ibice by'imashini z'umwuka.
Urugero, igihe ibitaro byo mu Butaliyani byari bikeneye cyane za valve zo guhumeka, maze abakozi baho bakaba badashobora kuzishyira mu gihe, ikigo cyo muri ako gace cyakoresheje ubuhanga bwo guhumeka maze cyandika za valve 100 zari zikenewe mu ijoro rimwe.
Nyuma y'icyorezo cya COVID-19, ibitekerezo by'ubuhendanyi n'amakuru y'ibinyoma ku byerekeranye n'aho iki cyorezo cyaturutse, urugero, kwirinda, kwivuza n'ibindi byangombwa by'ubwandu byagiye byiganje kuri interineti.
Abantu bagaragaye bafite amateka yo kwanduzanya virusi n'izindi nyamaswa.
Ubushakashatsi bwasuzumye ibimenyetso bya virusi mu ngurube, ibyatsi n'ibindi, ntibwashoboye.
Nta muti cyangwa urukingo rwemewe kuvurwa iyi ndwara.
Ubushakashatsi mpuzamahanga ku bijyanye n'inkingo za COVID-19 bwatangiye gukorwa n'imiryango ya leta, abanyeshuri n'abakora mu by'inganda.
Muri Werurwe, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryatangije icyiswe "Igerageza rya SOLIDARITE" ryo kwiga ingaruka z'imiti ikoreshwa mu kurwanya virusi ya B, bikaba byaratumye habaho icyizere gikomeye cy'uko iyi miti izavura.
Nta rukingo rwigeze rugaragara, ariko inzego nyinshi zirimo zirakora ibishoboka byose kugira ngo zitere imbere inkingo zemeza.
Igikorwa cya mbere cyakozwe ku SARS-CoV cyakozwe mu buryo bwa SARS-CoV na SARS-CoV-2 byombi bikoresha ACE2 mu kwinjira mu ngirabuzimafatizo z'abantu.
Hari uburyo butatu bwo gukingira abantu bugomba gukurikiranwa.
Icya mbere, abashakashatsi bifuza gukora urukingo rwa virusi yose.
Gukoresha virusi nk'iyi, yaba ifite ubukana cyangwa idafite, bigamije kwihutisha igisubizo cy'ubushobozi bw'umubiri mu kurwanya COVID-19.
Uburyo bwa kabiri, urukingo rw'udupira, rushaka gukora urukingo rutuma umubiri w'umuntu ugira ibyiyumvo ku bipimo by'ubwoko bwa virusi.
Mu gihe cya SARS-CoV-2, ubu bushakashatsi bwibanze kuri poroteyine ya S-spicules ituma virusi igera ku cyuma cyakira ACE2.
Uburyo bwa gatatu ni bwa mbere bwo gukingira abantu hakoreshejwe urukingo rwa ADN cyangwa RNA (inkingo zigezweho zo gukingira).
Inkingo zigeragejwe hakoreshejwe ubwo buryo zigomba kuba zishinzwe ubuziranenge n'umutekano. Ku ya 16 Werurwe 2020, igeragezwa rya mbere ry'urukingo ryatangijwe n'abakozi bane b'abakorerabushake i Seattle.
Urukingo ntirugira kode y'ibanze y'ubwandu, ahubwo rwinjizwa mu virusi itera indwara. Kwiyongera kw'imbaraga z'umubiri ushingiye ku rukingo rw'umubiri byitezwe ko mu gihe cy'intambara bishobora kuba ari impamvu yo guteza imbere urukingo rwa SARS-COV-2, ariko ibyo biracyari impaka.
Ibizamini byo kwa muganga birenga 300 ni byo biri gukorwa muri Mata 2020.
Ibizamini birindwi biri kwiga ku miti yemewe ya malariya, harimo bine by'imiti yitwa hydroxychloroquine cyangwa chloroquine.
Imiti igabanya ubukana bwa virusi ni yo ifite uruhare runini mu bushakashatsi bwakozwe n'Abashinwa, hamwe n'ibizamini icyenda byo mu cyiciro cya III bya Remdesivir mu bihugu byinshi bizatanga raporo mu mpera za Mata.
Isesengura ry'imikorere y'ibanze ry'ikigo cy'ubuvuzi cy'urukingo rwa COVID-19 mu rwego rw'ubuvuzi bwemewe ryatangiye muri Mata 2020.Ibindi miti myinshi ya virusi iteganyijwe gukorwa iri gukorwa mu rwego rwo kuvura COVID-19, harimo remdesivir, chloroquine na hydroxychloroquine, lopinavir/ritonavir na lopinavir/ritonavir ifatanyije na interferon beta.
Ibimenyetso by'indwara ya remdesivir byatangiye kugaragara muri Werurwe 2020.
Imibereho myiza y'abaganga yarushijeho kwiyongera mu barwayi bahawe imiti y'indwara ya remdesivir.
Ibizamini byo kwa muganga byo mu cyiciro cya III birakorwa muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika, Ubushinwa n'u Butaliyani. Chloroquine, yakoreshejwe bwa mbere mu kuvura malariya, yagejejwe mu Bushinwa muri Gashyantare 2020, mu byiciro bya mbere.
Ariko kandi, hari icyizere cy'uko abahanga bazamenya uko ibyo bintu by'ingenzi by'ingenzi by'umuntu biba byarahindutse.
Abashinzwe ubuzima muri Koreya no mu Bushinwa batanze amabwiriza yo gukoresha chloroquine.
Ariko ikigo cya Wuhan cya Virology kivuga ko mu gihe umuntu ahabwa dose imwe ya gamma ku munsi, ebyiri muri zo ziba zifite ubukana bukomeye kandi zishobora kumwica.
Ku ya 28 Werurwe 2020, FDA yemeje imikoreshereze y'ubucuruzi ya hydroxychloroquine na chloroquine mu ibanga ry'ubuvuzi mu kuvura abarwayi ba COVID-19.Icyiciro cya 7 cy'ibanze cy'Ubushinwa cyongeyemo interféron, ribavirin cyangwa umifenovir mu kurwanya COVID-19.
Amakuru y'ibanze agaragaza ko ibipimo byinshi bya ribavirin ari ingenzi mu kurwanya SARS-CoV-2 mu cyumba.
Nitazoxanide yamaze gutangwa mu bushakashatsi bukurikira muri in vivo nyuma yo kugaragaza ibipimo byoroheje bya SARS-CoV-2 bibuza. Ubushakashatsi bugaragaza ko kwinjiza poroteyine ya protein ya mbere ikoreshwa na protease ya transmembrane ya serine 2 (TMPRSS2) bifite akamaro kanini ku kwinjiza kwa SARS-CoV-2 binyuze mu guhura na ACE2 receptor.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku miti ya chloroquine na hydroxychloroquine irimo cyangwa idafite azithromycin bufite aho bugarukira cyane ku buryo ubuyobozi bw'ubuvuzi butemera imiti itari mu bushakashatsi bukurikira. Oseltamivir ntabwo irwanya SARS-CoV-2 in vitro kandi nta ruhare ruzwi igira mu kuvura COVID-19.
Imvura y'ibicurane ishobora kuba ari indwara ikomeye cyane mu cyiciro cya nyuma cya COVID-19 ikomeye.
Ibi bigaragaza ko hydroxychloroquine ishobora kugira ubushobozi bwo kurwanya indwara z'imyakura. Tocilizumab yashyizwe mu nkunga y'ubuvuzi na Komisiyo y'Igihugu y'Ubuzima y'u Bushinwa nyuma yo kurangiza ubushakashatsi buto.
Ubu hakorwa igerageza ry'icyiciro cya 2 mu gihugu cyose mu Butaliyani, ridafite ibipimo byafashwe mu buryo bw'impanuka, nyuma yo kubona ibisubizo byiza ku barwayi bafite ubumuga bukomeye.
Iyo ifatanywe n'ibipimo by'amaraso bya seriyamu ya ferritin mu gupima indwara, bigamije kubuza ikura, bikaba byitezwe ko ari byo bituma abantu bake cyane bapfa.
Icyiciro cya mbere cy'igerageza interleukin-6 cyemejwe na FDA nyuma y'igerageza ry'ibanze ryo kuvura indwara y'impyiko z'imyakura (steroid refractory cytokine withdrawal syndrome) mu buryo butandukanye, mu 2017 mu buryo bw'ingirabuzimafatizo ya CAR T.
Kugeza ubu, nta bimenyetso bifatika kandi bigenzurwa bigaragaza ko tocilizumab ari umuti mwiza wa CRS.
Gushyira mu bantu bakwiriye intanga z'abanduye COVID-19 z'abanduye indwara zanduye kandi ziganjemo zavuye mu bushobozi bw'umubiri bwo kwirinda indwara, ni uburyo bwo gupima no kwanduza abantu mu buryo budafite urukingo.
Icyo gikoresho cyageragejwe ariko ntibyagize icyo bigeraho.
Kugabanya virusi ni uburyo bwitezwe ko buzakoreshwa mu kuvura abarwayi b'indwara z'ibyorezo bya SARS-CoV-2.
Ibindi bintu bishobora gukorwa, urugero nk'imiti y'ubumara n'imiti y'indwara z'ibice by'umubiri, bishobora gukoreshwa.
Hari ubundi buryo bwo kuvura abarwayi bukoreshwa mu buryo budafite ingaruka, urugero nko gukoresha abarwayi bafite ubumuga bwo ku mubiri bumwe, bugenda bwitezwa imbere.
Igisemburo cya seriyamu y'abarwayi bakize, mu gihe mu maraso y'umuntu harimo igice cy'umusemburo w'umuntu wakize kandi gifite udukoko tw'ubwoko bwihariye tw'iyo virusi, gishobora kongerwa bitewe n'uko habonetse umuti.
